%20very%20diverse.%20We%20cannot%20say%20anything%20about%20it.%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20get%20more%20than%20130%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20his%20party%20colleague%20Digvijaya%20Singh.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20transformation.%20People%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20CM%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20poll%20of%20Polls%2C%20an%20aggregate%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%2C%20indicates%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20wind%20up%20with%20124%20of%20the%20state's%20230%20seats%2C%20where%20the%20majority%20mark%20is%20116.%20The%20Congress%20may%20get%20102%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20script%20played%20out%20in%20neighbouring%20Chhattisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20only%20in%20the%20BJP%20camp%20--%20after%20almost%20all%20exit%20polls%20gave%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20an%20edge.%20NDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20%E2%80%93%20an%20aggregate%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20--%20indicated%20that%2049%20of%20the%20state's%2090%20seats%20can%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%2038%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExit%20polls%20have%20a%20limited%20size.%20The%20sample%20size%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20huge%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Arun%20Sao%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20roaming%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20the%20past%201.5%20years.%20I%20have%20gone%20to%20each%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20constituency%20and%20had%20conversations%20with%20people.%20On%20that%20basis%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20on%20December%203%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20come%20to%20power%20with%20a%20clear%20majority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20can%20have%20their%20way%20with%20exit%20polls.%20The%20BJP%20will%20form%20the%20government.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20that%20people%20want%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20BJP's%20Prem%20Prakash%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20claims%20and%20counterclaims%20were%20also%20strong%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20exit%20polls%20predicted%20the%20state%20will%20remain%20faithful%20to%20its%20revolving-door%20tradition%20and%20vote%20out%20the%20ruling%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExit%20polls%20indicate%20that%20'raaj%20nahi%20rivaz'%20(trend%2C%20not%20rule)%20is%20set%20to%20change%20in%20Rajasthan%20as%20the%20Congress%20is%20going%20to%20win%20a%20majority%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gourav%20Vallabh%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Congress%20which%20is%20hoping%20to%20buck%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanking%20on%20a%20marginally%20higher%20polling%20figure%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20insisted%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan%20want%20to%20end%20the%20Congress%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Rajasthan%20want%20freedom%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20given%20their%20record%20of%20corruption.%20The%20BJP%20is%20going%20to%20form%20the%20government%20with%20a%20majority%20in%20Rajasthan%20as%20well%20as%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJP%20MP%20Baba%20Balaknath%2C%20who%20is%20the%20party%20candidate%20from%20the%20Tijara%20assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20indicated%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20get%20104%20of%20the%20state's%20200%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%2085.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701369180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fmdv488s_madhya-pradesh-exit-polls-2023_625x300_30_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexit-poll-2023-chhattisgarh-madhya-pradesh-mizoram-rajasthan-telangana-assembly-election-jp-congress-brush-off-exit-poll-results-forward-winning-argum-4622860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Exit%20polls%20that%20predicted%20a%20primacy%20of%20Congress%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana%20and%20that%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20have%20been%20hotly%