0in%20power%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20state%20in%202014.%20NDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20--%20an%20aggregate%20of%20seven%20exit%20polls%20--%20shows%20the%20Congress%20ahead%20in%2062%20of%20the%20state's%20119%20seats%2C%20the%20BRS%20on%C2%A0%2044.%20The%20BJP%20can%20win%20seven%20seats%20and%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20AIMIM%20five%20seats.%20The%20majority%20mark%20stands%20at%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mizoram%2C%20an%20aggregate%20of%20six%20exit%20polls%20indicate%20a%20hung%20house.%20Two%20exit%20polls%20predict%20the%20BJP-MNF's%20ruling%20alliance%20have%20a%20slim%20chance%20of%20victory.%20Only%20one%20predict%20a%20sweep%20for%20the%20new%20party%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement%20(ZPM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExit%20polls%2C%20though%2C%20can%20often%20get%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fpollofpoll.html%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aggregate%20of%20nine%20exit%20polls%20on%20Chhattisgarh%20predict%20a%20second%20term%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banking%20on%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20report%20card%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20The%20number%20of%20seats%20allotted%20to%20the%20party%20has%20been%20within%20the%20margin%20of%20early%2040s%20to%20mid-50s.%20The%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%2090-seat%20state%20stands%20at%2046.%20NDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20indicates%20that%2049%20seats%20can%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%2038%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fexitpoll_embed.html%3Fstatenm%3DCHH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeighbouring%20Madhya%20P