the%20200-member%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20election%20had%C2%A0%20taken%20place%20on%20199%20seats%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20the%20majority%20mark%20will%20be%20101.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20indicates%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20get%20104%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%2085.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fexitpoll_embed.html%3Fstatenm%3DRAJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2040-seat%20Mizoram%2C%20only%20two%20of%20six%20exit%20polls%20predict%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%2C%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%2C%20might%20make%20it%20to%20the%20seat%20of%20power%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aggregate%20of%20six%20exit%20polls%20indicates%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20can%20get%2015%20seats%2C%20the%20new%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement%20(ZPM)%2017%2C%20which%20could%20put%20Congress%2C%20expected%20to%20win%20seven%20seats%2C%20in%20the%20position%20of%20the%20kingmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chances%20of%20hung%20house%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20run%20high%2C%20with%20a%20multi-cornered%20contest%20that%20included%20the%20rising%20ZPM%2C%20which%20projected%20a%20young%20face%20for%20the%20state's%20top%20job.%20All%20exit%20polls%20have%20given%20the%20new%20party%20a%20chunk%20of%20seats%2C%20pushing%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20third%20spot%20in%20the%20state.%20India-Today-Axis%20My%20India%20predicts%20a%20sweep%20for%20the%20ZPM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20which%20also%20joined%20the%20race%2C%20could%20also%20bleed%20votes%20for%20the%20MNF%2C%20which%20won%2026%20of%20the%2040%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20election..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fexitpoll_embed.html%3Fstatenm%3DMIZ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20real%20sweet%20spot%20in%20this%20election%20could%20be%20Telangana%2C%20next-door%20to%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20it%20won%20a%20huge%20victory%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20beating%20the%20BJP%20hollow.%20The%20party%20had%20launched%20a%20high-octane%20campaign%20in%20Telangana%20since%2C%20under%20the%20upbeat%20leadership%20of%20its%20young%20state%20chief%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20has%20been%20out%20of%20the%20Congress's%20reach%20since%202014%2C%20when%20the%20state%20was%20carved%20out%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20despite%20its%20facilitating%20the%20formation%20from%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%2C%20who%20led%20the%20statehood%20agitation%2C%20heading%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20--%20now%20renamed%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20in%20keeping%20with%20its%20leader's%20national%20ambitions%20--%20there%20seemed%20little%20scope%20for%20the%20party%20to%20be%20dislodged%20from%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ndtv.com%2Fe%2Fassembly%2F2023%2Fdecember%2Fexitpoll%2Fexitpoll_embed.html%3Fstatenm%3DTG%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22description%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20votes%20for%20this%20round%20of%20elections%2C%20dubbed%20the%20semi-final%20before%20the%20next%20year's%20general%20election%2C%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20are%20expected%20to%20impact%20not%20just%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20hoping%20for%20a%20third%20straight%20term%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20positive%20outcome%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana%20can%20even%20raise%20its%20stocks%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20giving%20it%20more