orld-africa-67577038.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20hostages%3A%20Relief%20as%20Thai%20hostage%20is%20reunited%20with%20family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701358987000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F4401%2Fproduction%2F_131890471_p0gwws0z.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-67579435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pornsawan%20Pinakalo%20fell%20to%20his%20knees%20when%20he%20was%20greeted%20by%20his%20father%20after%20nearly%2050%20days%20in%20captivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-67579435%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Will%20Get%20Top%20Job%20If%20Congress%20Wins%20Chhattisgarh%3F%20TS%20Singh%20Deo%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20almost%20every%20exit%20poll%20giving%20the%20Congress%20an%20edge%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20state's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20TS%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20said%20while%20the%20numbers%20have%20come%20as%20a%20relief%2C%20he%20believes%20the%20party%20will%20win%2060%20of%20the%20state's%2090%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Deo%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20him%20becoming%20chief%20minister%20if%20the%20numbers%20come%20down%20significantly%20from%20the%2068%20the%20party%20had%20won%20last%20time.%20He%20said%20all%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20sat%20together%20and%20decided%20not%20to%20leave%20any%20room%20for%20speculation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20leader%2C%20who%20had%20a%20feud%20with%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20over%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%2C%20also%20candidly%20spoke%20about%20the%20problems%20that%20the%20party%20had%20faced%20because%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20one-line%20resolution%20to%20the%20high%20command%20and%20we%20will%20be%20together%20behind%20whoever%20they%20decide%20to%20give%20the%20responsibility%20as%20chief%20minister.%20We%20will%20not%20fall%20into%20this%20trap%20of%20speculation%20and%20groupism.%20We%20suffered%20on%20this%20count%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years...%20this%20two-and-a-half%2C%20two-and-a-half%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20big%20burden.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20situation%20and%20led%20to%20many%20situations%20which%20were%20unpalatable.%20We%20don't%20want%20a%20repeat%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Deo%20was%20referring%20to%20a%20claim%20that%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20had%20agreed%20to%20a%20rotational%20chief%20ministership%20when%20the%20party%20had%20won%20in%202018.%20After%20he%20was%20appointed%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20June%2C%20however%2C%20the%20leader%20had%20said%20he%20had%20never%20spoken%20of%20a%20rotational%20formula%20and%20that%20it%20was%20a%20creation%20of%20the%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorruption%20Allegations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20highlighted%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20%C2%A0especially%20related%20to%20the%20Mahadev%20App%20case%20-%20and%20whether%20they%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20exit%20polls%20showing%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20at%20least%2030%20seats%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%2015%20it%20won%20in%202018%2C%20Mr%20Deo%20said%20the%20opposition%20party's%20tally%20in%20the%20last%20elections%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20unusual%20number%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20not%20the%20true%20picture%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20but%20they%20somehow%20managed%20to%20get%20just%2015%20seats.%20That%20was%20the%20way%20the%20numbers%20played%20out%20eventually.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20was%20expecting%20the%20BJP%20to%20be%20around%2035%20(seats)%20because%20that%20is%20the%20vote%20share%20that%20we%20have%20had%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20is%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20state%20elections%2C%20both%20parties%20enjoy%20a%20minimum%20vote%20share%20of%2030-32%25%20and%20it%20is%20the%2010%25%20floating%20vote%20share%20that%20gives%20the%20majority%20to%20either%20party%20in%20any%20election.%20That%20will%20be%20the%20deciding%20factor%2C%20where%20this%20vote%20goes.%20We%20will%20wait%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECensus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20Caste%20Census%20being%20pushed%20for%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20most%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20said%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20not%20been%20affected%20much%20by%20caste%20or%20religious%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20the%20OBC%20census%20is%20a%20medium%20through%20which%20we%20can%20frame%20our%20policies.%20If%20we%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20real%20demographic%20is%20in%20society%2C%20how%20do%20you%20target%20developmental%20projects%3F%20So%2C%20that%20is%20the%20basic%20commitment%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20undertaken....%20It%20was%20done%20in%201931%20and%20then%20we%20went%20away%20from%20that%20for%20various%20reasons.%20It%20was%20done%20again%20in%202012%2C%20but%20those%20figures%20were%20not%20released.%20Why%20should%20we%20not%20have%20those%20figures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Deo%20also%20said%20that%2C%20based%20on%20the%20feedback%20he%20has%20got%2C%20the%20Congress%20should%20win%20130%20of%20230%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20form%20a%20government%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20exit%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Deo%20pointed%20out%20that%20every%20agency%20is%20putting%20out%20a%20different%20figure.%20%26quot%3BI%2C%20personally%2C%20don't%20take%20it%20at%20face%20value.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20common%20number%20that%20comes%20through%20various%20channels%2C%20and%20everybody%20will%20say%20they%20did%20it%20scientifically...%20We%20should%20wait.%20It%20gives%20you%20a%20trend%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20an%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701358920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7qg2iag8_ts-singh-deo_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-be-chief-minister-if-congress-wins-chhattisgarh-ts-singh-deo-says-4622423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20almost%20every%20exit%20poll%20giving%20the%20Congress%20an%20edge%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20state's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20TS%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20said%20while%20the%20numbers%20have%20come%20as%20a%20relief%2C%20he%20believes%20the%20party%20will%20win%2060%20of%20the%20state's%2090%20seats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-be-chief-minister-if-congress-wins-chhattisgarh-ts-singh-deo-says-4622423%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-be-chief-minister-if-congress-wins-chhattisgarh-ts-singh-deo-says-4622423%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-be-chief-minister-if-congress-wins-chhattisgarh-ts-singh-deo-says-4622423%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Henry%20Kissinger%3A%20Man%20who%20despised%20India%2C%20but%20ended%20up%20...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701358885000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105633330%2Cimgsize-693079.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhenry-kissinger-man-who-once-despised-india-but-ended-up-kissing-up-to-new-delhi%2Farticleshow%2F105633237.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%2