3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105626831.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAn%20FBI%20agent%20was%20carjacked%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20but%20emerged%20unharmed.%20The%20stolen%20vehicle%20was%20found%20later.%20The%20incident%20highlights%20the%20increasing%20carjacking%20crisis%20in%20the%20city%2C%20where%20over%20900%20cases%20were%20reported%20in%202023.%2077%25%20of%20these%20carjackings%20involved%20firearms.%20Carjackings%20have%20surged%20by%20104%25%20this%20year%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20overall%20rise%20in%20violent%20crime%20in%20Washington.%20The%20incident%20reinforces%20the%20need%20for%20improved%20security%20measures%20and%20interventions%20to%20address%20the%20escalating%20carjacking%20wave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffbi-agent-becomes-latest-victim-amid-rising-tide-of-carjackings-in-washington-dc%2Farticleshow%2F105626831.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffbi-agent-becomes-latest-victim-amid-rising-tide-of-carjackings-in-washington-dc%2Famp_articleshow%2F105626831.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffbi-agent-becomes-latest-victim-amid-rising-tide-of-carjackings-in-washington-dc%2Famp_articleshow%2F105626831.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Archeological%20Body%20Gets%2010%20More%20Days%20To%20Submit%20Report%20On%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Varanasi%20court%20has%20given%20a%2010-day%20extension%20to%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20to%20file%20a%20report%20on%20its%20findings%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20premises.%20This%20is%20the%20fourth%20time%20the%20archaeological%20body%20got%20an%20extension%20to%20file%20the%20report%20on%20its%20scientific%20survey%2C%20which%20was%20completed%20a%20month%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20ASI%20had%20asked%20for%2021%20days'%20extension%2C%20which%20was%20opposed%20by%20the%20mosque%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20was%20ordered%20by%20a%20Varanasi%20court%20on%20July%2021%2C%20after%20four%20women%20sought%20permission%20to%20pray%20at%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20last%20year%2C%20the%20court%20ordered%20a%20video%20survey%20of%20the%20complex%20on%20basis%20of%20their%20petition.%20The%20survey%20conducted%20in%20May%20revealed%20a%20structure%20in%20the%20Wuzukhana%2C%20that%20the%20petitioners%20claimed%20was%20a%20'shivling'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wuzuhana%20has%20been%20kept%20out%20f%20bounds%20for%20the%20scientific%20survey%20by%20an%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20is%20located%20next%20to%20the%20iconic%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple.%20Right-wing%20activists%20claim%20a%20temple%20existed%20at%20the%20site%20and%20was%20demolished%20in%20the%2017th%20century%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ayodhya%20and%20Mathura%2C%20Gyanvapi%20is%20the%20third%20temple-mosque%20row%2C%20which%20propelled%20the%20BJP%20to%20national%20prominence%20in%20the%20'80s%20and%20'90s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20is%20already%20being%20heard%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20on%20the%20Sri%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi-Shahi%20Masjid%20Idgah%20dispute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20claim%20that%20it%20has%20been%20built%20at%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20within%20the%2013.37-acre%20premises%20of%20the%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20petitions%20have%20been%20filed%20in%20local%20courts%20seeking%20the%20shifting%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701344580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frlrlma4_gyanvapi-mosque-ani_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farcheologica