ps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FDCb5UaA9pE%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FDCb5UaA9pE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20PETA%20(%40peta)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpeta%2Fstatus%2F1729678462552523173%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20campaigns%20were%20launched%20across%20the%20world%20to%20relocate%20the%20elephant%20amid%20concerns%20about%20her%20lonely%20life%20and%20treatment%20by%20zoo%20authorities%20but%20she%20spent%20decades%20in%20solitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaul%20McCartney%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20The%20Beatles%2C%20had%20written%20to%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Philippines%20in%202012%20pushing%20for%20the%20Asian%20elephant's%20early%20release%20and%20transfer%20to%20another%20country%2C%20but%20authorities%20warned%20against%20any%20such%20move%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Fsoutheast-asia%2Fmali-manila-zoo-saddest-elephant-dies-b2455324.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20spoke%20to%20the%20zoo's%20chief%20vet%20Dr%20Heinrich%20Patrick%20Pena-Domingo%2C%20who%20said%20that%20Mali%20was%20noticed%20rubbing%20her%20trunk%20against%20a%20wall%20constantly%2C%20suggesting%20she%20was%20in%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elephant's%20condition%20worsened%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20breathing%20heavily.%20An%20autopsy%20later%20revealed%20that%20Mali%20had%20pancreatic%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67563146%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mali%20was%20gifted%20to%20the%20Philippine's%20former%20first%20lady%20Imelda%20Marcos%20by%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20in%201981.%20The%20elephant%20was%2011%20months%20old%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20spent%20her%20early%20days%20with%20another%20elephant%2C%20Shiva%2C%20who%20had%20been%20living%20in%20the%20zoo%20since%201977%20and%20who%20died%20in%201990.%20Mali%20lived%20alone%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701341340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Faf5mi1qo_mali-the-elephant-dies_625x300_30_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmali-worlds-saddest-elephant-dies-in-manila-zoo-4621245%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20elephant%20was%20gifted%20to%20the%20Philippine's%20former%20first%20lady%20Imelda%20Marcos%20by%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20in%201981.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmali-worlds-saddest-elephant-dies-in-manila-zoo-4621245%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmali-worlds-saddest-elephant-dies-in-manila-zoo-4621245%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmali-worlds-saddest-elephant-dies-in-manila-zoo-4621245%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22American%20angst%3A%20Survey%20reveals%2070%25%20feel%20US%20heading%20in%20wrong%20direction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701340709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105624010%2Cimgsize-33402.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Famerican-angst-survey-reveals-70-feel-us-heading-in-wrong-direction%2Farticleshow%2F105623924.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105623924.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20annual%20Reagan%20National%20Defense%20Survey%20reveals%20that%20only%2025%25%20of%20Americans%20believe%20the%20United%20States%20is%20heading%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20shift%20from%20previous%20years.%20Congress%20f