s%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10509%2Fproduction%2F_131852866_gettyimages-1810136785-594x594.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67571742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20temporary%20ceasefire%20will%20last%20another%20day%20after%20it%20was%20extended%20just%20before%20it%20was%20due%20to%20expire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67571742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67571742.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67571742.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raids%2C%20Seizures%2C%20Searches%3A%20How%20Central%20Agencies%20Have%20Taken%20Poll%20Position%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30145920%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20polls%20saw%20yet%20another%20round%20of%20central%20investigation%20agencies%20descending%20on%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20one%20case%20or%20another.%20The%20timing%20of%20such%20raids%20were%20questioned%20by%20many%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20when%20investigation%20agencies%20are%20increasingly%20being%20seen%20as%20aiding%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20political%20interests.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20to%20conduct%20searches%20and%20seizures%20of%20property%20without%20a%20formal%20complaint%20in%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20cases%2C%20effectively%20presuming%20the%20accused%20person%20to%20be%20guilty.%20A%20three-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20A.M.%20Khanwilkar%20broadened%20the%20investigative%20powers%20of%20the%20ED%20by%20upholding%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20several%20contentious%20sections%20of%20the%20Act.%20Since%20then%2C%20however%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20targeted%20opposition%20leaders%20particularly%20during%20election%20campaigns%2C%20raising%20grave%20doubts%20about%20its%20autonomy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EED%E2%80%99s%20latest%20round%20of%20searches%20and%20seizures%20have%2C%20again%2C%20been%20directed%20against%20important%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20states%20which%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20high-pitched%20electoral%20battles%2C%20with%20BJP%20among%20the%20principal%20players.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20examples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20raided%20the%20Jaipur%20and%20Sikar%20premises%20of%20Pradesh%20Congress%20President%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%2C%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20October%2C%20when%20he%20was%20busy%20campaigning.%20No%20official%20statement%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20ED%20but%20it%20came%20to%20be%20known%20that%20the%20searches%20were%20conducted%20in%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20houses%20in%20an%20alleged%20teachers%E2%80%99s%20entrance%20exam%20leak%20case.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20him%2C%20properties%20of%20another%20Congress%20MLA%20%E2%80%93%20Om%20Prakash%20Hudla%2C%20from%20the%20Mahua%20seat%20in%20Dausa%20%E2%80%93%20were%20also%20searched.%20Interestingly%2C%20paper%20leaks%20in%20service%20selection%20entrance%20examinations%20was%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20issues%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20been%20raising%20against%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20Congress%20state%20government.%20Later%20in%20November%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20son%20Avinash%20and%20Abhilash%20also%20received%20summons%20from%20the%20ED.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20son%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20also%20received%20ED%E2%80%99s%20summons%2C%20prompting%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20compare%20the%20ED%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctiddi%20dal%E2%80%9D%20(locusts)%20obeying%20their%20masters%2C%20meaning%20the%20BJP.%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20been%20conducting%20raids%20against%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20workers%2C%20and%20those%20associated%20with%20the%20party%2C%20almost%20everyday%20amidst%20the%20election%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20raids%2C%20Dotasra%20said%20that%20the%20ED%20officials%20could%20not%20find%20any%20cash%20or%20illegal%20documents%20from%20his%20premises%2C%20and%20yet%20seized%20his%20and%20his%20sons%E2%80%99%20phones%20and%20pen%20drive.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20search%20warrant%20was%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20son%20Avinash%2C%20who%20is%20an%20accounts%20officer.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20been%20probing%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20links%20with%20a%20coaching%20institute%20Kalam%20academy%2C%20but%20the%20PCC%20chief%20said%20neither%20he%20nor%20his%20sons%20have%20any%20connection%20with%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20son%20was%20also%20reportedly%20called%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA)%20case%20against%20a%20hospitality%20group%20called%20Triton%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20early%20November%2C%20the%20ED%20also%20conducted%20searches%20of%2025%20premises%20in%20an%20alleged%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20scam%20being%20probed%20under%20the%20PMLA.%20The%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20is%20a%20union%20government%20scheme%20to%20provide%20potable%20water%20through%20tap%20in%20every%20household.The%20ED%20raided%20state%20minister%20Mahesh%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20properties%20and%20the%20premises%20of%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20in%20the%20public%20health%20engineering%20department%20Subodh%20Agarwal.%20Along%20with%20him%2C%20multiple%20other%20raids%20by%20the%20ED%20happened%20in%20the%20properties%20of%20engineers%2C%20contractors%2C%20government%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20scam%20was%20reported%20when%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20filed%20an%20FIR%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena%20who%20alleged%20a%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20scam%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme.%20The%20FIR%20alleged%20that%20two%20companies%20Shree%20Shyam%20Tubewell%20Company%20and%20Shree%20Ganpati%20Tubewell%20Company%20paid%20bribes%20to%20public%20servants%20to%20cover%20up%20irregularities%20and%20inflate%20bills%20for%20the%20work%20done%20by%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20July%202020%2C%20when%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20was%20facing%20revolt%20from%20his%20colleague%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20raided%20the%20premises%20associated%20with%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Agrasen%20Gehlot%2C%20and%20his%20company%20Anupam%20Krishi%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20diversion%20of%20fertilisers%20during%202007-2009.%20Agrasen%20has%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20many%20times%2C%20even%20as%20the%20case%20continues%20to%20drag%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChhattisgarh%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%E2%80%99s%20searches%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20began%20as%20early%20as%20August%2C%202023%20when%20premises%20of%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20political%20adviser%20and%20former%20journalist%20Vinod%20Verma%20and%20two%20Officers%20on%20Special%20Duty%20were%20raided%20in%20Raipur%20and%20Durg.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20following%20a%20seizure%20of%20Rs%2014.92%20crore%20in%20Raipur%20and%20Durg%2C%20the%20ED%20named%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20its%20statement%20as%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20Rs%20508%20crore%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case%20just%20four%20days%20before%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20on%20November%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20itself%20was%20curious%20in%20the%20way%20it%20unfolded.%20First%2C%20the%20ED%20claimed%20that%20the%20app%E2%80%99s%20promoters%20Saurabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20two%20Bhilai-based%20residents%20who%20ran%20a%20juice%20shop%2C%20ran%20a%20huge%20online%20betting%20nexus%20with%20the%20help%20of%20several%20franchises.%20The%20ED%20also%20questioned%20several%20Hindi%20film%20industry%20actors%20in%20the%20case%20that%20was%20being%20probed%20since%20July%2C%202022.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20Congress%20connection%2C%20nowhere%20did%20it%20present%20itself.%20However%2C%20just%20before%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20released%20a%20video%20clip%20in%20which%20a%20person%20named%20Shubham%20Soni%20claimed%20to%20be%20real%20owner%20of%20the%20online%20betting%20app%20and%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20paid%20Rs%20508%20crore%20as%20bribe%20to%20Baghel%20through%20his%20media%20advisor%20and%20an%20IPS%20officer%20to%20seek%20protection%20from%20any%20punitive%20action.%20Soni%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20told%20by%20Baghel%20to%20flee%20to%20Dubai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20ED%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-ed-contrasting-approach-bhupesh-baghel-devendra-tomar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereleased%20a%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20naming%20Baghel%20as%20an%20accused%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20video%20released%20by%20Soni.%20It%20also%20claimed%20that%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20name%20propped%20up%20in%20a%20statement%20made%20by%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccash%20courier%E2%80%9D%20arrested%20in%20Raipur%20with%20possession%20of%20around%20Rs%205%20crore.%20But%20the%20agency%20added%20that%20all%20these%20accusations%20%E2%80%9Care%20a%20subject%20matter%20of%20investigation%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20slammed%20such%20accusations%20as%20serving%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20interests%20and%20tarnishing%20the%20popular%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20image%2C%20Baghel%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20never%20met%20any%20of%20the%20three%20people%20%E2%80%93%20Chandrakar%2C%20Uppal%2C%20and%20Soni%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20ED%20mentioned.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20if%20there%20was%20any%20merit%20to%20the%20accusations%2C%20the%20ED%20should%20show%20concrete%20proof.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStartlingly%2C%20days%20after%20the%20elections%20were%20over%2C%20Asim%20Das%2C%20the%20alleged%20cash%20courier%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20Raipur%20with%20around%20Rs%205%20crore%20and%20whose%20statement%20was%20the%20basis%20of%20implicating%20Baghel%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case%2C%20wrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-betting-app-case-courier-held-by-ed-denies-delivering-cash-to-politicians%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20letter%20to%20the%20Special%20Court%2C%20Raipur%20and%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20Director%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saying%20that%20he%20never%20delivered%20any%20cash%20to%20politicians%20and%20that%20he%20was%20being%20framed%20in%20a%20conspiracy.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20had%20visited%20Dubai%20to%20meet%20his%20childhood%20friend%20Soni%20regarding%20investments%20in%20his%20construction%20business%20and%20indicated%20that%20the%20cash%20seized%20from%20him%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20betting%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20ED%20also%20arrested%20state%20ASI%20Chandrabhushan%20Verma%2C%20businessman%20Satish%20Chandrakar%2C%20and%20alleged%20hawala%20operators%20Anil%20Dammani%20and%20Suni%20Dammani.%20The%20ED%2C%20following%20the%20raids%2C%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Chigh-ranking%20officials%20connected%20with%20the%20CMO%20(Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office)%20received%20kickbacks%20to%20allow%20illegal%20online%20betting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20raids%20in%20other%20cases%2C%20too%2C%20by%20the%20ED.%20The%20agency%20conducted%20searches%20and%20seizures%20in%2015%20different%20places%20in%20October%20when%20it%20allied%20that%20state%20rice%20millers%20association%20in%20cahoots%20with%20officers%20of%20state%E2%80%99s%20Marketing%20Federation%20Ltd%20(MARKFED)%20illegally%20increased%20the%20price%20of%20paddy%20to%20an%20exorbitant%20Rs%20120%20per%20quintal%20after%20%E2%80%9Chigher%20powers%E2%80%9D%20were%20bribed%20with%20Rs%20175%20crore.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20had%20made%20similar%20raids%20and%20arrested%20persons%20in%20the%20coal%20levy%20commission%20case%2C%20allegedly%20involving%20Rs%20540%20crore%20and%20illegal%20liquor%20sale%20which%20allegedly%20cost%20the%20state%20exchequer%20Rs%202160%20crore.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20ED%20claimed%20that%20the%20illegal%20money%20went%20to%20%E2%80%9Ca%20political%20party%E2%80%9D%20but%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20the%20accusation.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20persons%20said%20to%20be%20close%20aides%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20Baghel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fcongress-leaders-under-ed-s-scanner-in-chhattisgarh-101678190531626.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20arrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20made%20an%20arrest%20in%20August%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20354%20crore%20bank%20fraud%20case%20involving%20many%20influential%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20including%20Ratul%20Puri%2C%20the%20nephew%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20Kamal%20Nath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20had%20booked%20Ratul%20Puri%2C%20his%20father%20Deepak%20Puri%2C%20mother%20Nita%20in%20another%20case%20that%20accused%20Moser%20Baer%20India%20Ltd%2C%20a%20CD%20manufacturing%20company%20owned%20by%20Puri%2C%20and%20its%20promoters%20of%20bank%20fraud%20from%20a%20loan%20taken%20from%20the%20Central%20Bank%20of%20India.%20The%20ED%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20following%20the%20same%20case%20against%20Puri.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20in%20August%202023%20also%20arrested%20a%20former%20relationship%20manager%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20Singapore%20Nitin%20Bhatnagar%20in%20the%20PMLA%20case%20against%20Moser%20Baer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20leaders%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20were%20trying%20to%20indict%20multiple%20Congress%20workers%20and%20associates%20under%20the%20scanner%20to%20help%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20elections..%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20getting%20information%20through%20newspapers%20that%20the%20offices%20of%20Income%20Tax%20and%20ED%20are%20being%20opened%20at%20different%20places%E2%80%A6Officials%20are%20being%20posted%E2%80%A6They%20are%20raiding%20the%20ruling%20(Congress)%20regime%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20in%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20ED%2C%20IT%20offices%20are%20being%20opened%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20should%20raid%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20ministers%20and%20their%20favourite%20officers%2C%20but%20as%20per%20the%20news%20being%20received%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20target%20the%20Congress%20and%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20MP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETelangana%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Telangana%2C%20the%20ED%20sent%20fresh%20summons%20to%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20MLC%20K.%20Kavitha%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20K.Chandrasekhar%20Rao%2C%20in%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20case%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20She%20has%20received%20ED%E2%80%99s%20summons%20in%20the%20case%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20new%20excise%20policy%20introduced%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20in%20which%20849%20liquor%20shops%20were%20allocated%20to%20private%20firms%20was%20scrapped%20by%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20after%20Delhi%20L-G%20Vinay%20Kumar%20Saxena%20recommended%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%2C%20citing%20irregularities%20in%20the%20policy%E2%80%99s%20implementation.%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20have%20already%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20alleged%20that%20Kavitha%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CSouth%20Group%E2%80%9D%20that%20paid%20at%20least%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20bribes%20to%20AAP%20through%20AAP%20worker%20and%20businessman%20Vijay%20Nair%20who%20has%20already%20been%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20Kavitha%2C%20various%20other%20BRS%20functionaries%20also%20faced%20ED%E2%80%99s%20raids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20week%20before%20polling%2C%20the%20ED%20also%20swooped%20down%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-polls-ed-raids-properties-of-congress-candidate-g-vivek%2Farticleshow%2F105373501.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MLA%20candidate%20G.Vivek%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20Rs%208%20crore%20transaction%20between%20his%20company%20and%20one%20Vigilance%20Security%20Services%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20The%20ED%20claimed%20that%20the%20transferred%20amount%20originated%20from%20an%20unidentified%20bank%20account.%20Searches%20were%20conducted%20on%20November%2020%20at%20various%20locations%20owned%20by%20Vivek%2C%20Congress%20MLA%20candidate%20from%20Chennu%20seat.%20Incidentally%2C%20Vivek%20had%20recently%20quit%20the%20BJP%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%20and%20is%20the%20richest%20candidate%20in%20the%20fray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20I-T%20department%20also%20conducted%20searches%20at%20Vivek%E2%80%99s%20premises.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20I-T%20department%20and%20the%20ED%20had%20raided%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F021123%2Fincome-tax-raids-on-congress-and-brs-leaders-in-hyderabad.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20premises%20of%20Congress%20candidates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Kichannagari%20Lakshma%20Reddy%20of%20Maheswaram%20and%20Ponguleti%20Srinivasa%20Reddy%20of%20Palair%20in%20different%20cases%20of%20financial%20fraud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECuriously%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20most%20of%20these%20raids%20as%20vehicles%20to%20advance%20its%20anti-corruption%20political%20rhetoric%20and%20have%20attacked%20the%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls.%20In%20many%20of%20these%20cases%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20more%20than%20the%20ED%2C%20has%20revealed%20the%20charges%20against%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20its%20press%20briefings.%20How%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20get%20the%20details%20even%20before%20the%20ED%20revealed%20them%20was%20debated%20in%20political%20circles%20quite%20vigorously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20didn%E2%80%99t%20conduct%20any%20raids%20in%20Mizoram.%20The%20election%20in%20the%20state%20is%20between%20the%20incumbent%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20or%20MNF%20and%20the%20other%20seven-party%20regional%20alliance%2C%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement.%20The%20BJP%20has%20one%20MLA%20in%20the%20state%20at%20present%20and%20analysts%20say%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20major%20electoral%20stakes%20here%2C%20as%20it%20depends%20more%20or%20less%20on%20its%20regional%20allies.%20Narendra%20Modi%20cancelled%20his%20election%20rally%20here.%20The%20Congress%20used%20to%20be%20an%20important%20player%20but%20has%20now%20shrunk%2C%20with%20just%205%20MLAs%20in%20the%20outgoing%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20earlier%20reported%20that%20almost%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2F95-of-political-leaders-investigated-by-cbi-ed-are-opposition-leaders-non-bjp-parties-tell-supreme-court-224653%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E95%25%20of%20the%20cases%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20probed%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20against%20political%20leaders%20are%20from%20the%20opposition.%20Although%20the%20ED%20claims%20that%20it%20has%20a%20high%20conviction%20rate%20of%2096%25%2C%20the%20figures%20appear%20to%20be%20misplaced%20if%20one%20factors%20in%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20it%20has%20closed%20since%202005.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20registered%205%2C906%20cases%20until%20March%202023%20but%20completed%20the%20probe%20and%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fed-is-claiming-it-has-a-high-conviction-rate-but-its-closed-only-25-cases-since-2005%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eonly%201%2C142%20cases%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20which%20it%20has%20disposed%20of%20only%2025%20cases%2C%20a%20mere%200.42%20of%20the%20total%20number%20of%20cases.%20Of%20those%2025%20cases%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20managed%20convictions%20in%2024%20cases%2C%20which%20is%20around%2096%25%20conviction%20rate%20as%20claimed%20by%20the%20agency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3Edenied%20all%20allegations%20of%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fsince-2014-4-fold-jump-in-ed-cases-against-politicians-95-per-cent-are-from-opposition-8163060%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20four-fold%20jump%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20ED%20cases%20since%202014%3B%2095%25%20of%20those%20cases%20are%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fed-scanner-aap-bjp-satyendar-jain-sanjay-raut-chidambaram-1956298-2022-05-31%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopposition%20leaders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701340232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30145920%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-opposition-leaders-raids-ed-cbi-income-tax%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ED%E2%80%99s%20latest%20round%20of%20searches%20and%20seizures%20have%2C%20again%2C%20been%20directed%20against%20important%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20states%20which%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20high-pitched%20electoral%20battles%2C%20with%20BJP%20among%20the%20principal%20players.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-opposition-leaders-raids-ed-cbi-income-tax%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rema%3A%20Calm%20down%20singer%20cancels%20December%20shows%20for%20health%20reasons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701339381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbrand