%20south%2C%20and%20inequalities%20between%20the%20global%20north%20and%20the%20global%20south.%20The%20influential%20theory%20that%20emerged%20from%20Western%20academia%20was%20that%20of%20global%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20for%20the%20global%20justice%20debate%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%201972%20paper%20by%20the%20utilitarian%20philosopher%20Peter%20Singer%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpersonal.lse.ac.uk%2Frobert49%2Fteaching%2Fmm%2Farticles%2FSinger_1972Famine.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Famine%2C%20Affluence%20and%20Morality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20reputed%20journal%20%3Cem%3EPhilosophy%20and%20Public%20Affairs%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer-300x248.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer-1024x846.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125539%2FPeter-Singer.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687067%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22248%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Mal%20Vickers%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY%20SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20suffering%20and%20death%20from%20a%20lack%20of%20food%2C%20shelter%20and%20medical%20care%20are%20simply%20bad.%20If%20it%20is%20within%20the%20power%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20affluent%20West%20to%20prevent%20something%20bad%20from%20happening%2C%20without%20sacrificing%20anything%20of%20comparable%20moral%20importance%2C%20they%20are%20morally%20obliged%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20not%20matter%20that%20people%20who%20suffer%20for%20avoidable%20reasons%20are%20distant%20or%20proximate%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20are%20fellow%20nationals%20or%20needy%20foreigners.%20The%20need%20of%20strangers%20is%20as%20morally%20compelling%20as%20the%20need%20of%20neighbours%20or%20fellow%20citizens.%C2%A0%20It%20also%20does%20not%20matter%20that%20other%20people%20do%20or%20do%20not%20contribute%20their%20mite%20to%20the%20alleviation%20of%20poverty%20and%20misery%3B%20individuals%20should%20take%20on%20this%20moral%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20donating%20to%20famine%20relief%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20charity%20but%20that%20of%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20later%20work%20titled%20%3Cem%3EOne%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singer%20argued%20that%20since%20the%20world%20is%20interlinked%2C%20we%20need%20a%20transborder%20global%20ethics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%2C%20he%20suggested%2C%20that%20you%20walk%20along%20a%20pond%20and%20see%20a%20small%20child%20in%20danger%20of%20drowning.%20It%20would%20be%20morally%20wrong%20not%20to%20try%20to%20save%20the%20child%20even%20if%20the%20suit%20we%20wear%20gets%20wet%20and%20is%20ruined.%20The%20cost%20is%20small%20compared%20to%20the%20good%20of%20saving%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20have%20special%20feelings%20for%20those%20we%20love%20or%20those%20who%20are%20close%20to%20us%2C%20but%20this%20need%20not%20prevent%20us%20from%20helping%20others.%20There%20is%20no%20great%20difference%20between%20compatriots%20and%20the%20distant%20needy.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20middle-class%20American%20should%20give%20to%20the%20global%20poor%20something%20like%20one%20percent%20of%20his%20or%20her%20annual%20income.%20Basically%2C%20Singer%20focused%20on%20moral%20choices%20between%20spending%20on%20personal%20desires%20and%20helping%20the%20needy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20political%20theorists%20living%20and%20working%20in%20what%20was%20once%20called%20the%20third%20world%2C%20were%20considerably%20sceptical%2C%20even%20outraged%20at%20this%20newest%20version%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98white%20man%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20we%20in%20the%20global%20south%20afford%20to%20wait%20for%20citizens%20of%20the%20West%20to%20recognise%20their%20obligations%20to%20the%20distant%20needy%3F%20Should%20we%20be%20doing%20so%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestine-palestinians-and-the-western-liberals-burden%5C%22%3EPalestine%2C%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Western%20Liberal%E2%80%99s%20Burden%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20it%20not%20dependent%20on%20charity.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20wrenched%20from%20the%20recalcitrant%20fists%20of%20elites%20through%20mass%20struggles%20and%20agitation.%20Despite%20some%20acrimonious%20challenges%20to%20the%20universality%20of%20global%20justice%20(for%20we%20who%20inhabit%20the%20world%20of%20the%20distant%20needy%20had%20no%20role%20to%20play%20in%20these%20theories%20except%20as%20a%20recipient)%20the%20debate%20taught%20us%20a%20valuable%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20need%20to%20expand%20the%20notion%20of%20duties%20and%20concern%20to%20people%20who%20live%20outside%20our%20borders.%20We%20should%20adopt%20a%20cosmopolitan%20approach%20towards%20human%20well-being.%20Cosmopolitanism%20moderates%20nationalist%20ambitions%20and%20opens%20many%20doors%20to%20solidarity%20across%20national%20borders.%20This%20is%20its%20virtue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20second%20decade%20of%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20the%20context%20of%20political%20theory%20had%20dramatically%20changed.%20Across%20the%20world%2C%20the%20extreme%20right-wing%20came%20to%20command%20power.%20Under%20the%20impact%20of%20right-wing%20extremism%2C%20cosmopolitanism%20was%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20window%2C%20and%20societies%20closed%20their%20doors%20and%20windows.%20They%20were%20now%20preoccupied%20with%20hostility%20against%20minorities%2C%20immigrants%2C%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%20and%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imaginary%20enemy%2C%20right-wing%20populists%20told%20us%2C%20does%20not%20lurk%20on%20our%20border%20alone%2C%20it%20is%20within%20our%20own%20borders.%20Our%20fellow-citizens%20and%20those%20who%20sought%20citizenship%20became%20our%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20has%20the%20shift%20from%20cosmopolitanism%20to%20a%20narrow%20and%20ugly%20nationalism%20taken%20place%20so%20rapidly%2C%20except%20in%20the%20period%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20consolidation%20of%20German%20Nazism%2C%20which%20was%20openly%20hostile%20to%20the%20internationalism%20of%20the%20Left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notion%20of%20obligation%20towards%20the%20%E2%80%98distant%20needy%E2%80%99%20or%20even%20the%20%E2%80%98proximate%20needy%E2%80%99%20who%20did%20not%20belong%20to%20our%20religious%20community%2C%20were%20replaced%20by%20duty%20towards%20our%20own%20people%20with%20whom%20we%20were%20bound%20by%20ties%20of%20religion%20or%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distinction%20between%20cosmopolitanism%20and%20a%20nationalism%20that%20urges%20us%20to%20confine%20our%20loyalties%20to%20our%20own%2C%20came%20to%20mind%20as%20we%20read%20of%20another%20victory%20of%20the%20extreme%20right%20in%20Europe%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-geert-wilders-poll-victory-in-the-netherlands-reflects-european-radical-right-populism%5C%22%3Ethe%20success%20of%20Geert%20Wilder%E2%80%99s%20Party%20for%20Freedom%20(PVV)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160248%2FWilders-bezoekt-Rotterdam-DSC_0218_cropped-300x187.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160248%2FWilders-bezoekt-Rotterdam-DSC_0218_cropped-300x187.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23160248%2FWilders-bezoekt-Rotterdam-DSC_0218_cropped.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686091%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22187%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGeert%20Wilders.%20Photo%3A%20Wouter%20Engler%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PVV%2C%20winning%2037%20of%20the%2050%20seats%20in%20parliament%2C%20is%20now%20a%20majority%20party.%20The%20Netherlands%2C%20for%20long%20identified%20with%20centrist%20politics%2C%20has%20now%20turned%20to%20the%20right.%20The%20implications%20are%20grim%20because%20Wilder%20is%20a%20polarising%20figure.%20He%20is%20against%20immigration%2C%20Islam%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%20He%20has%20opposed%20the%20construction%20of%20mosques%2C%20advocates%20strict%20control%20on%20drugs%20and%20urges%20a%20reduction%20in%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20decades%2C%20most%20of%20Europe%20has%20been%20taken%20over%20by%20right-wing%20populists.%20Viktor%20Orban%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Hungary%2C%20has%20directed%20the%20erection%20of%20fences%20to%20keep%20out%20refugees%20from%20war-torn%20Syria%2C%20captured%20the%20judiciary%20and%20other%20institutions%2C%20has%20openly%20encouraged%20crony%20capitalism%2C%20incorporated%20Christian%20values%20into%20the%20Constitution%20and%20is%20reportedly%20against%20gender%20studies%20in%20university%20curricula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20written%20the%20standard%20text%20of%20right-wing%20authoritarianism%2Fpopulism%3A%20institutional%20capture%20and%20democratic%20backsliding.%20Right-wing%20authoritarianism%20has%20transformed%20former%20liberal%20democracies%20into%20illiberal%20electoral%20democracies.%20All%20that%20remains%20on%20the%20political%20landscape%20is%20elections.%20The%20script%20is%20surely%20familiar%20to%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20examples%20that%20come%20to%20us%20from%20Europe.%20One%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-will-its-first-far-right-leader-since-wwii-mean-for-italy%5C%22%3Erise%20of%20Georgia%20Meloni%E2%80%99s%20Brothers%20of%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Italy%3A%20nationalistic%20to%20the%20core%2C%20anti-immigrant%20and%20obsessed%20with%20state%20sovereignty.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffrance-far-right-marine-le-pen-2022-election%5C%22%3EThe%20increasing%20prominence%20of%20Marine%20Le%20Penn%E2%80%99s%20National%20Rally%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20France%20promises%20that%20another%20right-wing%20populist%20will%20come%20to%20power%20at%20some%20point%20in%20a%20country%20that%20expanded%20and%20popularised%20democracy%20first%20conceived%20of%20and%20implemented%20in%20Greece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20countless%20other%20examples%20of%20right-wing%20populists%3A%20Netanyahu%20in%20Israel%20and%20Putin%20in%20Russia%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20former%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20current%20leaders%20of%20India.%20They%20insistently%20subvert%20democracy%2C%20erode%20liberal%20ideas%20of%20obligation%20to%20others%20simply%20because%20they%20are%20human%20beings%2C%20dismiss%20inclusiveness%20and%20pluralism%2C%20mock%20equality%20and%20dignity%2C%20tolerance%20and%20secularism%2C%20corrode%20institutions%2C%20curtail%20civil%20liberties%20and%20openly%20head-hunt%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%2C%20the%20right%20head-hunts%20refugees%20who%20have%20been%20driven%20from%20their%20homes%20by%20wars%20not%20of%20their%20own%20making.%20Europe%2C%20once%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Renaissance%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20humanism%20and%20modern%20political%20values%20such%20as%20liberty%2C%20equality%20and%20fraternity%2C%20has%20become%20a%20graveyard%20of%20all%20these%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-right-wing-is-on-the-rise-globally%5C%22%3EThe%20Right%20Wing%20Is%20on%20the%20Rise%20Globally%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20to%20misrecognise%20the%20fact%20that%20European%20countries%20violated%20their%20own%20values%20while%20colonising%20our%20world.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%2C%20it%20requires%20a%20different%20story.%20The%20issue%20is%20as%20follows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Why%20does%20Globalisation%20Fuel%20Populism%3F%E2%80%99%20This%20is%20the%20title%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3Ewell-known%20essay%3C%2Fa%3E%20authored%20by%20the%20economist%20Dani%20Rodrik%20of%20Harvard%20University%20in%20the%202021%20%3Cem%3EAnnual%20Review%20of%20Economics%3C%2Fem%3E.%20There%20is%2C%20he%20suggests%2C%20compelling%20evidence%20that%20globalisation%20shocks%2C%20often%20working%20through%20culture%20and%20identity%2C%20have%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20driving%20up%20support%20for%20populist%20movements%20of%20the%20right-wing%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20integration%20has%20produced%20domestic%20disintegration%20in%20many%20countries.%20The%20populist%20response%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20a%20mostly%20right-wing%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20factors%20that%20intensify%20uncertainty%20amidst%20globalisation.%20Across%20the%20globe%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20consequences%20of%20globalisation%20is%20the%20dismantling%20of%20the%20welfare%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20whatever%20social%20legislation%20was%20passed%20in%20the%202004-2014%20period%20of%20UPA%20rule%20has%20been%20pulled%20to%20pieces%20by%20the%20NDA%20regime.%20The%20religious%20right-wing%20in%20the%20country%20has%20put%20into%20place%20a%20highly%20personalised%20system%20of%20the%20grant%20of%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20welfare%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20aspect%20of%20an%20appropriative%20state%3B%20it%20amounts%20to%20little%20more%20than%20the%20gift%20giving%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20grain%20and%20a%20little%20money.%20The%20grateful%20consumer%20is%20expected%20to%20show%20her%2C%20well%20gratitude%2C%20by%20casting%20a%20vote%20for%20the%20gift-giver.%20The%20citizen%2C%20as%20Yamini%20Aiyar%20puts%20it%2C%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3Elabharthi%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dismantling%20of%20the%20welfare%20state%20that%20had%20been%20built%20brick-by-brick%20by%20social%20struggles%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20a%20sympathetic%20judiciary%2C%20has%20led%20to%20tremendous%20insecurity.%20Privatisation%20of%20assets%20to%20industrial%20houses%20openly%20aligned%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20gravely%20reduced%20government%20jobs.%20Whatever%20jobs%20are%20left%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20have%20become%20the%20object%20of%20fervent%20desire%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20promise%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20above%20all%2C%20globalisation%20brings%20a%20sense%20of%20homelessness%20because%20we%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20definite%20identity%20in%20an%20interconnected%20world.%20This%20was%20an%20identity%20that%20was%20carefully%20fashioned%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20our%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInto%20this%20vacuum%20stepped%20in%20the%20religious%20right%2C%20flourishing%20the%20pennant%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20versus%20them%E2%80%99%2C%20advocating%20a%20strong%20state%20and%20an%20even%20stronger%20leader%2C%20and%20urging%20us%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20is%20cultural%20homogeneity%20and%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20people%20who%20do%20not%20fit%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20populists%20are%20dangerous%20because%20their%20politics%20is%20extremist%2C%20their%20ideology%20exclusionary%2C%20their%20enmity%20to%20those%20who%20do%20not%20belong%20palpable%2C%20their%20religious%20rhetoric%20cynical%20and%20opportunistic%2C%20and%20their%20chief%20desire%20to%20divide%20people%20so%20that%20they%20can%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20only%20a%20little%20over%20three%20decades%20that%20political%20theorists%20were%20speaking%20of%20a%20cosmopolitanism%2C%20a%20concept%20that%20Indians%20were%20already%20familiar%20with%20through%20the%20creative%20writings%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20we%20speak%20the%20language%20of%20provocation%2C%20taboos%2C%20censorship%2C%20coercion%20and%20bullying.%20Globalisation%20has%20battered%20the%20notion%20of%20obligation%20to%20each%20other%20simply%20because%20as%20human%20beings%20we%20owe%20each%20other.%20We%20now%20live%20in%20a%20Hobbesian%20state%20of%20nature%2C%20which%20is%20a%20state%20of%20war%20of%20all%20against%20all.%20We%20wait%20for%20a%20Leviathan%20to%20restore%20and%20reinforce%20our%20social%20contract%20%E2%80%93%20our%20Constitution%20that%20promises%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fneera-chandhoke%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ENeera%20Chandhoke%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0was%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Delhi%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701338451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30133927%2FGeert-Wilders.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnarrow-nationalism-has-won-over-cosmopolitanism-again-this-time-in-the-netherlands%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22International%20integration%20has%20produced%20domestic%20disintegration%20in%20many%20countries.%20The%20populist%20response%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20a%20mostly%20right-wing%20form.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnarrow-nationalism-has-won-over-cosmopolitanism-again-this-time-in-the-netherlands%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Court%20Filing%20That%20Links%20Assassination%20Attempt%20to%20Indian%20Official%20'Matter%20of%20Concern'%3A%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22182025%2Fdownload-11.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20the%20linking%20of%20an%20Indian%20official%20in%20a%20case%20filed%20by%20US%20prosecutors%20against%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20for%20directing%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20assassinate%20a%20US%20citizen%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmatter%20of%20concern%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2FOn%2520the%2520evening%2520of%2520June%252018%2520after%2520Hardeep%2520Singh%2520Nijjar%2520was%2520gunned%2520down%2520outside%2520a%2520Sikh%2520temple%2520in%2520Canada%2C%2520%5C%22%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20US%20prosecutors%20filed%20a%2015-page%20detailed%20indictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleging%20that%20an%20%E2%80%9Cidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%E2%80%9D%20was%20behind%20a%20plot%20of%20assassinate%20a%20US%20citizen%20who%20runs%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20group%20that%20is%20banned%20by%20India.%20While%20the%20indictment%20does%20not%20name%20the%20target%2C%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20the%20attempt%20was%20made%20on%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20head%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Sikhs%20for%20Justice%E2%80%99%20NGO%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20filings%20charged%20Indian%20resident%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20had%20allegedly%20been%20the%20go-between%20between%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20(%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99)%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98criminal%20associate%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20actually%20working%20for%20US%20law%20enforcement%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20post-indictment%20reaction%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20the%20case%20against%20an%20individual%20that%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20court%2C%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20We%20have%20said%2C%20let%20me%20reiterate%2C%20that%20this%20is%20also%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20characterisation%20of%20the%20US%20concerns%20as%20being%20related%20to%20criminal%20activity.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20nexus%20between%20organised%20crime%2C%20trafficking%2C%20gunrunning%20and%20extremists%20at%20an%20international%20level%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20for%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20organisations%20to%20consider%20and%20it%20is%20for%20that%20reason%20that%20a%20high-level%20inquiry%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20and%20we%20will%20be%20guided%20by%20its%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20said%20at%20a%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20had%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20just%20ahead%20of%20release%20of%20the%20fresh%20indictment%2C%20that%20India%20had%20set%20up%20an%20inquiry%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20US%20%E2%80%98plot%E2%80%99%20on%20November%2018.%20The%20government%20had%20not%20spoken%20of%20the%20committee%20when%20the%20US%20%E2%80%98concerns%E2%80%99%20were%20first%20reported%20by%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20and%20then%20confirmed%20by%20the%20White%20House%20%E2%80%93%20on%20November%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20have%20informed%20earlier%2C%20during%20the%20course%20of%20discussions%20with%20the%20US%20on%20bilateral%20security%20cooperation%2C%20the%20US%20side%20shared%20some%20inputs%20pertaining%20to%20nexus%20between%20organised%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnecessary%20follow-up%20action%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20Enquiry%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20follow-up%2C%20Bagchi%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20share%20any%20further%20information%20on%20such%20security%20matters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrasting%20India%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20concerns%20raised%20by%20US%20and%20Canada%20about%20targeting%20of%20their%20citizens%2C%20Bagchi%20continued%20with%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20tough%20stance%20against%20Ottawa.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20so%20far%20as%20Canada%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20they%20have%20consistently%20given%20space%20to%20anti-India%20extremists%20and%20that%20is%20actually%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20issue.%20Our%20diplomatic%20representatives%20in%20Canada%20have%20borne%20the%20brunt%20of%20this.%20So%2C%20we%20expect%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20to%20live%20up%20to%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations.%20We%20have%20also%20seen%20interference%20by%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs%20and%20that%20is%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20filed%20by%20US%20federal%20prosecutor%20clearly%20indicated%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20had%20been%20aware%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98big%20target%E2%80%99%20in%20Canada%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20June%2018%2C%20following%20the%20shooting%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20Canada%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Fus-attorney-announces-charges-connection-foiled-plot-assassinate-us-citizen-new-york%5C%22%3Ethe%20indictment%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CCC-1%20sent%20GUPTA%20a%20video%20clip%20showing%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20bloody%20body%20slumped%20in%20his%20vehicle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20significant%20point%20in%20the%20court%20filing%20as%20it%20indicated%20that%20US%20authorities%20had%20obtained%20electronic%20communications%20that%20linked%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20directly%20to%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20made%20this%20claim%20of%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20September%20this%20year%2C%20which%20New%20Delhi%20had%20instantly%20dismissed.%20The%20Union%20government%20took%20subsequent%20steps%20that%20led%20to%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20leaving%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701337983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22182025%2Fdownload-11.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-court-filing-that-links-assassination-attempt-to-indian-official-matter-of-concern-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20the%20case%20against%20an%20individual%20that%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20court%2C%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20We%20have%20said%2C%20let%20me%20reiterate%2C%20that%20this%20is%20also%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-court-filing-that-links-assassination-attempt-to-indian-official-matter-of-concern-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rural%20Consumption%20Sees%20Slowest%20Growth%20in%20Eight%20Quarters%20During%20July-September%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F13125046%2Fagriculture-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rural%20consumption%20experienced%20a%20mere%200.5%25%20year-on-year%20growth%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20marking%20the%20slowest%20pace%20in%20eight%20quarters%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20contrasts%20with%20urban%20consumption%2C%20which%20grew%207.4%25%20in%20July-September%202023%2C%20the%20highest%20rate%20in%20four%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20Motilal%20Oswal%20Financial%20Services%20(MOFSL)%2C%20the%20tepid%20consumption%20scenario%20in%20rural%20areas%20was%20mainly%20led%20by%20sharply%20deteriorating%20reservoir%20level%2C%20the%20first%20fall%20in%20two-wheeler%20sales%20in%20six%20quarters%2C%20and%20first%20contraction%20in%20fertilizer%20sales%20in%20seven%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETractor%20sales%20also%20decreased%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20quarter%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20decline%20in%20real%20farm%20exports%20for%20the%20fourth%20straight%20quarter%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-rural-consumption-tepid-q2-growth-slowest-in-8-quarters-3321097%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20analysis%20is%20also%20supported%20by%20the%20MGNREGA%20(Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act)%20data.%20Employment%20demand%20by%20households%20under%20MGNREGA%20was%20much%20higher%20in%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%20FY24%20compared%20with%20FY23%20and%20FY18-20%20average%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2022%20million%20people%20demanded%20employment%20under%20MGNREGA%20each%20in%20September%20and%20October%2C%2010-18%25%20higher%20than%20in%20the%20corresponding%20months%20of%20FY23%2C%20and%2026-31%25%20higher%20than%20the%20pre-COVID%20period%2C%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHDFC%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20economist%20Swati%20Arora%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20that%20uneven%20monsoon%20led%20to%20crop%20damage%2C%20which%20weighed%20on%20rural%20consumption.%20She%20adde