20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20June%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20employee%20gave%20Gupta%20the%20home%20address%20of%20Pannun%2C%20his%20phone%20numbers%20and%20details%20about%20his%20daily%20conduct%2C%20including%20surveillance%20photos%2C%20which%20Gupta%20passed%20along%20to%20the%20undercover%20DEA%20agent%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20quotes%20Michael%20Kugelman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Wilson%20Center%E2%80%99s%20South%20Asia%20Institute%2C%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20dependence%20on%20India%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20China%20problem%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20balm%20at%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20most%20cases%2C%20if%20Washington%20accuses%20a%20foreign%20government%20of%20staging%20an%20assassination%20on%20its%20soil%2C%20U.S.%20relations%20with%20that%20government%20would%20plunge%20into%20crisis.%20But%20the%20relationship%20with%20India%20is%20a%20special%20case.%20%E2%80%A6%20It%E2%80%99s%20notable%20that%20once%20the%20administration%20found%20out%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20scale%20down%20engagement%20with%20India.%20High-level%20meetings%20went%20on%20as%20scheduled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Three%20such%20killings%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fus-unseals-indictment-sikh-killings-1.7043428%5C%22%3ECBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bp%5Derhaps%20the%20most%20surprising%20allegation%20in%20the%20murder-for-hire%20indictment%20filed%20in%20New%20York%20state%20against%20Indian%20national%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20is%20a%20claim%20that%20there%20were%20plans%20to%20carry%20out%20three%20such%20killings%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20details%20of%20the%20indictment%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%2C%20the%20CBC%20report%20says%20the%20plan%20to%20kill%20Pannu%20%E2%80%9Cchanged%20on%20June%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20when%20masked%20gunmen%20murdered%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20British%20Columbia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20which%20adds%20that%20this%20made%20the%20killing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpriority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20mentions%20how%20the%20indictment%20has%20it%20that%20the%20Indian%20official%2C%20in%20a%20phone%20call%2C%20allegedly%20noted%20that%20a%20different%20hitman%20had%20handled%20it%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20to%20%5Bthe%20undercover%20officer%5D%20this%20job%2C%20so%20some%20other%20guy%20did%20this%20job%20%E2%80%A6%20in%20Canada.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AFP%20news%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20231129-us-charges-indian-man-with-plotting-hit-on-sikh-separatist%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20as%20having%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20news%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20United%20States%20further%20underscores%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20talking%20about%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20which%20is%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20take%20this%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%20needs%20to%20work%20with%20us%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20getting%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701326809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30121410%2FUntitled-design-12-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Findia-us-pannun-nijjar-foreign-media%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'In%20most%20cases%2C%20if%20Washington%20accuses%20a%20foreign%20government%20of%20staging%20an%20assassination%20on%20its%20soil%2C%20U.S.%20relations%20with%20that%20government%20would%20plunge%20into%20crisis.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Findia-us-pannun-nijjar-foreign-media%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Navigating%20PM-KISAN%3A%20A%20Deep%20Dive%20into%20Digital%20Challenges%20Faced%20by%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F08200430%2Fimage1-2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PM-KISAN%20Samman%20Nidhi%20Scheme%2C%20initiated%20in%202019%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20crucial%20financial%20support%20system%20for%20Indian%20farmers%2C%20offering%20an%20annual%20Rs%206%2C000%20subsidy%20distributed%20in%20three%20instalments%20directly%20to%20their%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllocating%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbudgets%2Fparliament%2Fdemand-for-grants-2023-24-analysis-agriculture-and-farmers-welfare%5C%22%3E50%25%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%20Welfare%E2%80%99s%20budget%20to%20the%20PMKISAN%20scheme%20in%202022-23%20and%202023-24%3C%2Fa%3E%20underscores%20the%20high%20priority%20the%20Union%20government%20places%20on%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2022%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%20Welfare%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20introduced%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1959461%5C%22%3EAI%20Chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20PMKISAN%20Scheme.%20This%20chatbot%2C%20among%20other%20functions%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%20farmers%20with%20prompt%2C%20clear%20and%20accurate%20responses%20to%20their%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20discuss%20the%20obstacles%20encountered%20by%20those%20using%20the%20scheme%20within%20its%20digital%20framework.%20We%20trace%20changes%20in%20two%20specific%20aspects%20of%20the%20digital%20framework%3A%20access%20to%20information%2C%20and%20changing%20compliances.%20The%20changes%20in%20both%20aspects%20since%202019%20impact%20not%20just%20%E2%80%98entitlement%20holders%E2%80%99%20experience%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20but%20also%20potentially%20hamper%20the%20seamless%20flow%20of%20benefits.%20Using%20case%20studies%20gathered%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(AP)%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Telangana%2C%20we%20illustrate%20the%20struggles%20of%20farmers%20and%20local%20officials%20in%20navigating%20PMKISAN%E2%80%99s%20digital%20landscape.%20This%20journey%20underscores%20the%20necessity%20for%20streamlined%20and%20accessible%20information%20systems%20to%20ensure%20any%20welfare%20programme%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccess%20to%20information%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20begin%20with%20the%20story%20of%20Pongo%20Donno%2C%20an%20Adivasi%20farmer%20from%20Odisha%2C%20whose%20journey%20to%20uncover%20his%20PMKISAN%20status%20illustrates%20how%20changes%20in%20the%20system%20have%20transformed%20his%20efforts%20to%20access%20this%20information%20over%20time.%20Donno%E2%80%99s%20primary%20concern%20is%20to%20stay%20informed%20about%20his%20payment%20status%2C%20the%20associated%20bank%20accounts%2C%20entitled%20and%20received%20instalments%2C%20as%20well%20as%20reasons%20for%20non-payment%20if%20any%20instalment%20is%20missed.%20This%20information%20is%20valuable%20for%20farmers%2C%20and%20is%20also%20the%20basic%20expectation%20from%20any%20portal%20providing%20information%20on%20a%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20the%20essential%20requirement%20for%20farmers%20%E2%80%93%20understanding%20their%20PMKISAN%20status%20%E2%80%93%20has%20undergone%20four%20changes.%20Just%20as%20farmers%20and%20officials%20understood%20one%20change%2C%20another%20system%20emerged.%20In%20Donno%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20initial%20process%20relied%20on%20Aadhaar%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmkisan.gov.in%2FBeneficiaryStatus_New.aspx%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98KNOW%20YOUR%20STATUS%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Formerly%20%E2%80%98Beneficiary%20Status%E2%80%99)%20verification.%20Local%20officials%20would%20verify%20his%20PMKISAN%20status%20using%20his%20Aadhaar%20and%20provide%20the%20necessary%20information.%20They%20would%20also%20navigate%20through%20other%20details%20on%20PMKISAN%E2%80%99s%20Management%20Information%20System%20(MIS)%20to%20provide%20any%20missing%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Underperformed%20in%20Developing%20the%20Rural%20Economy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-underperform-developing-rural-economy%5C%22%3EThe%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Underperformed%20in%20Developing%20the%20Rural%20Economy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20method%20later%20shifted%20towards%20verification%20through%20registration%20numbers%20or%20phone%20numbers%2C%20and%20later%20evolved%20to%20using%20registration%20numbers%20exclusively.%20For%20Donno%2C%20these%20methods%20proved%20futile%20as%20he%20lacked%20access%20to%20his%20registration%20number%20or%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20functioning%20phone%20number%20linked%20to%20his%20PMKISAN%20account%2C%20which%20is%20the%20situation%20for%20many%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20system%20evolved%20to%20allow%20access%20to%20the%20registration%20number%20by%20using%20Aadhaar%20details.%20However%2C%20acquiring%20registration%20numbers%20remained%20a%20cumbersome%20task%20for%20Donno.%20He%20has%20to%20navigate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cknow%20your%20registration%20number%E2%80%9D%20option%20on%20MIS.%20Upon%20entering%20the%20OTP%20sent%20to%20his%20Aadhaar-linked%20mobile%2C%20Donno%20could%20access%20his%20PMKISAN%20registration%20number.%20This%20system%20proved%20less%20effective%20for%20farmers%20like%20him%20residing%20in%20areas%20with%20no%20network%20coverage%2C%20rendering%20the%20Aadhaar-phone%20link%20insignificant.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20phone%20number%20linked%20with%20the%20PMKISAN%20account%20option%20offered%20little%20help%20to%20Donno%20due%20to%20the%20frequent%20non-functionality%20of%20his%20mobile.%20The%20option%20of%20a%20simple%20paper%20trail%20would%20have%20resolved%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20farmers%20like%20Donno.%20This%20holds%20true%20for%20many%20entitlement-holders%20that%20reside%20in%20remote%2C%20network-poor%20areas%2C%20especially%20tribal%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmkisan.gov.in%2FDocuments%2FRevisedPM-KISANOperationalGuidelines(English).pdf%5C%22%3EPMKISAN%20operational%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98beneficiary%20lists%E2%80%99%20should%20be%20posted%20at%20Panchayats%20for%20transparency.%20States%2FUTs%20should%20send%20SMS%20notifications%20to%20beneficiaries%20upon%20benefit%20sanction.%20But%20such%20measures%20are%20rarely%20followed.%20Even%20when%20the%20beneficiary%20lists%20are%20showcased%2C%20they%20lack%20payment%20details%20or%20reasons%20for%20non-payment%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20ineffectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20with%20changing%20compliances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20in%20the%20compliance%20structure%20of%20PMKISAN%20fund%20transfers%20also%20significantly%20impacted%20farmers%20like%20%E2%80%98Korra%20Jimbo%E2%80%99%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Originally%20registering%20in%202019%20without%20submitting%20his%20Aadhaar%2C%20Jimbo%20faced%20halted%20payments%20post%20the%20third%20instalment%20due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmkisan.gov.in%2FDocuments%2FRevisedFAQ.pdf%5C%22%3Enewly-mandatory%20Aadhaar%20authentication%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Cross-verifying%20Aadhaar%20names%20with%20the%20PMKISAN%20list%20caused%20nationwide%20payment%20disruptions%2C%20leaving%20over%2097%2C000%20farmers%20in%20AP%20unpaid%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flibtech.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FAP_PM_Kisan_Sep21.pdf%5C%22%3ELibTech%20India%20study%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompliance%20evolution%20didn%E2%80%99t%20halt%20there.%20In%20December%202021%2C%20E-Kyc%20emerged%20on%20ground%2C%20requiring%20farmers%20to%20submit%20biometrics%20for%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20either%20at%20the%20geographically%20scarce%20Customer%20Service%20Centre%20points%20or%20through%20the%20PMKISAN%20website%20via%20linked%20phone%20numbers%2C%20challenging%20those%20with%20unlinked%20Aadhaar-phone%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20came%20across%20several%20instances%20of%20farmers%20meeting%20the%20mandatory%20criteria%20of%20a%20bank%20account%20registered%20for%20Aadhaar-based%20payments%2C%20completed%20EKyc%2C%20and%20proper%20land%20seeding%20status%2C%20who%20faced%20challenges%20in%20receiving%20PMKISAN%20payments.%20Investigations%20showed%20their%20instalments%20were%20halted%20citing%20vague%20reasons%20like%20%E2%80%9CUntraceable%20Beneficiary%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%98Old%20district%20to%20new%20district%20transfer%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20lacked%20clarity%20on%20the%20specific%20reasons%20and%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20from%20Account%20Based%20payment%20to%20Aadhaar%20Based%20Payment%20System%20(ABPS)%20in%20March%202022%20further%20complicated%20matters.%20Mangiben%E2%80%99s%20case%20from%20Gujarat%20illustrates%20how%20the%20transition%20from%20a%20simple%20account%20transfer%20system%20to%20the%20ABPS%20in%20PMKISAN%20caused%20problems.%20Despite%20previously%20receiving%20funds%20in%20a%20known%20bank%20account%2C%20Mangiben%20missed%20her%20last%20two%20payments%20without%20explanation.%20ABPS%20requires%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bank%20accounts%20to%20be%20linked%20with%20Aadhaar%20and%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20mapper.%20However%2C%20for%20farmers%20who%20are%20not%20eligible%20for%20ABPS%2C%20the%20MIS%20incorrectly%20displays%20%E2%80%98Aadhaar%20not%20linked%20to%20Bank%20account%2C%E2%80%99%20leading%20to%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELogin%20procedures%20for%20officials%20facilitating%20PMKISAN%20implementation%20have%20also%20evolved%2C%20from%20a%20straightforward%20user%20ID%20and%20password%20process%20to%20including%20OTPs.%20The%20Agricultural%20Department%20limited%20logins%20to%20NIC-registered%20officials%2C%20who%20were%20directed%20to%20download%20Kavach%2C%20an%20app%20generating%20OTPs%20for%20each%20login%20which%20was%20later%20rolled%20back.%20This%20convoluted%20procedure%20discouraged%20regular%20logins%20to%20address%20problems%20by%20local%20officials%2C%20further%20worsening%20challenges%20for%20vulnerable%20farmers.%20Though%20no%20clarity%20exists%20about%20the%20rationale%20behind%20the%20system%20changes%2C%20insights%20from%20official%20interviews%20suggest%20these%20modifications%20aim%20to%20prevent%20wrongful%20inclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20as%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20complex%20challenges%20posed%20by%20PMKISAN%E2%80%99s%20evolving%20compliance%20landscape%2C%20the%20introduction%20of%20technological%20solutions%20that%20reduce%20the%20hardships%20to%20people%20are%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20recognise%20that%20vulnerable%20sections%2C%20as%20highlighted%20in%20this%20article%2C%20often%20face%20digital%20disadvantages%20due%20to%20various%20reasons.%20Therefore%2C%20while%20embracing%20technological%20advancements%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20not%20to%20compromise%20offline%20systems%20that%20have%20traditionally%20served%20as%20a%20lifeline%20for%20those%20with%20limited%20digital%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20integration%20of%20AI%20Chatbots%20should%20complement%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20existing%20offline%20mechanisms.%20For%20farmers%20like%20Donno%20and%20Jimbo%2C%20grappling%20with%20network%20issues%20and%20changing%20digital%20requirements%2C%20maintaining%20robust%20offline%20support%20is%20essential.%20By%20adopting%20a%20balanced%20approach%20that%20harnesses%20the%20power%20of%20technology%20while%20safeguarding%20the%20accessibility%20of%20offline%20systems%2C%20we%20can%20ensure%20not%20only%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20social%20welfare%20programmes%20reach%20every%20corner%20of%20society%20but%20also%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20access%20their%20entitlements%2C%20leaving%20no%20one%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChakradhar%20Buddha%20and%20B.D.S.%20Kishore%20are%20affiliated%20with%20LibTech%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701325889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F08200430%2Fimage1-2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnavigating-pm-kisan-a-deep-dive-into-digital-challenges-faced-by-farmers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20embracing%20technological%20advancements%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20not%20to%20compromise%20offline%20systems%20that%20have%20traditionally%20served%20as%20a%20lifeline%20for%20those%20with%20limited%20digital%20access.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnavigating-pm-kisan-a-deep-dive-into-digital-challenges-faced-by-farmers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden%20takes%20fight%20to%20Trump%20ally%20in%20Colorado%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701325755000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105613650%2Cimgsize-156320.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-takes-fight-to-trump-ally-in-colorado%2Farticleshow%2F105613670.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105613670.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-takes-fight-to-trump-ally-in-colorado%2Farticleshow%2F105613670.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-takes-fight-to-trump-ally-in-colorado%2Famp_articleshow%2F105613670.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-takes-fight-to-trump-ally-in-colorado%2Famp_articleshow%2F105613670.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nepal%20Becomes%20First%20South%20Asian%20Country%20to%20Officially%20Recognise%20a%20Queer%20Marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F12171059%2FLGBT.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ENepal%20has%20become%20the%20first%20South%20Asian%20country%20to%20officially%20register%20a%20queer%20marriage.%20The%20registration%20took%20place%20in%20Lamjung%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fgandaki-province%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fnepal-becomes-second-country-in-asia-to-register-same-sex-marriage%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-seven-year%20old%20Surendra%20Pandey%20and%2037-year-old%20Maya%20Gurung%20registered%20their%20marriage%20five%20years%20after%20getting%20married%20at%20a%20temple%2C%20the%20portal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20in%20a%20restaurant%20and%20immediately%20liked%20each%20other.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20courtship%2C%20we%20moved%20in%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maya%20about%20their%20meeting%20around%20nine%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20our%20family%20and%20society%20did%20not%20accept%20us.%20We%20then%20moved%20to%20Kathmandu.%20Although%20we%20got%20married%20in%20a%20temple%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20our%20marriage%20was%20not%20legally%20recognised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDordi%20Rural%20Municipality%20chairman%20Yuvaraj%20Adhikari%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20registration%20request%20had%20been%20filed%20a%20week%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20marriage%20has%20been%20registered%20at%20the%20ward%20office%20after%20the%20Department%20of%20National%20ID%20and%20Civil%20Registration%20instructed%20it%20to%20register%20the%20marriage%20in%20the%20temporary%20record%20as%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20interim%20order%20until%20the%20formulation%20of%20a%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adhikari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20passed%20an%20interim%20order%20saying%20same-sex%20couples%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20register%20their%20marriages%20while%20a%20final%20decision%20is%20made%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERights%20activists%20have%20welcomed%20Surendra%20and%20Maya%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20registration.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20historic%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sunil%20Babu%20Pant%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Blue%20Diamond%20Society%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fnepal-registers-first-same-sex-marriage-historic-say-activists-2023-11-29%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20open%20the%20door%20for%20them%20to%20jointly%20open%20bank%20accounts%2C%20own%20and%20transfer%20property%20like%20just%20any%20other%20couples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701319908000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F12171059%2FLGBT.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flgbtqia%2Fnepal-becomes-first-south-asian-country-to-officially-recognise-a-queer-marriage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twenty-seven-year%20old%20Surendra%20Pandey%20and%2037-year-old%20Maya%20Gurung%20registered%20their%20marriage%20five%20years%20after%20getting%20married%20at%20a%20temple.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flgbtqia%2Fnepal-becomes-first-south-asian-country-to-officially-recognise-a-queer-marriage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30090551%2FUntitled-design-11-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3Eformal%20indictment%20in%20a%20New%20York%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%20and%20resident%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cothers%20known%20and%20unknown%E2%80%9D%2C%20for%20plotting%20the%20murder%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20a%20US%20citizen%20active%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Khalistan%20movement%E2%80%99%20contains%20a%20catena%20of%20allegations%20that%20are%20extremely%20damaging%20for%20the%20reputation%20of%20those%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20national%20security%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20summarise%20the%20most%20lethal%20aspects%20of%20the%20indictment%2C%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20in%20an%20intelligence%20or%20security%20agency%20who%20remains%20unnamed%20(except%20as%20%E2%80%98CC1%E2%80%99)%20%E2%80%93%20but%20whose%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20US%20law%20enforcement%20%E2%80%93%20engaged%20Gupta%20as%20a%20cut-out%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20in%20the%20US%20to%20kill%20Gurpatwant%20Pannun%20of%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice.%20Gupta%2C%20described%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20narcotics%20trafficker%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20DEA%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20criminal%20associate%20in%20the%20US%20who%20unfortunately%20happened%20to%20be%20a%20confidential%20source%2C%20or%20snitch%2C%20for%20the%20DEA.%20As%20often%20happens%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20snitch%20must%20have%20offered%20up%20this%20planned%20murder%20to%20his%20handlers%2C%20who%20then%20presumably%20roped%20in%20the%20FBI%20to%20deploy%20an%20undercover%20officer%20as%20the%20hitman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20a%20period%20of%20approximately%20two%20months%20%E2%80%93%20May%20and%20June%2C%202023%20%E2%80%93%20the%20confidential%20source%20and%20the%20undercover%20officer%20kept%20up%20the%20charade%20with%20Gupta%20and%20CC1%2C%20collecting%20electronic%20evidence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20messages%20exchanged%20over%20an%20encrypted%20app%2C%20photos%20and%20video%2C%20logging%20IP%20addresses%2C%20and%20also%20the%20handover%20of%20%2415%2C000%20as%20advance%20payment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20in%20case%20there%20is%20any%20doubt%20about%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20official%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20government%20agency%20he%20works%20for%2C%20the%20indictment%20says%20in%20black%20and%20white%3A%20%E2%80%9CCC-1%20was%20employed%20at%20all%20times%20relevant%20to%20this%20Indictment%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20resides%20in%20India%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20assassination%20plot%20from%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEncrypted%20communication%20cracked%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20worryingly%20for%20the%20Indian%20intelligence%20establishment%2C%20US%20investigators%20have%20been%20able%20to%20access%20encrypted%20messages%20exchanged%20between%20CC1%20and%20Gupta%20from%20early%20May%202023%2C%20i.e.%20even%20before%20the%20latter%20reached%20out%20to%20his%20criminal%20associate%20in%20the%20US%20to%20commission%20the%20hit.%20This%20means%20one%20of%20three%20things%2C%20none%20of%20which%20rebound%20to%20the%20credit%20of%20Indian%20tradecraft.%20First%2C%20that%20Gupta%20was%20indiscreet%20enough%20to%20carry%20devices%20containing%20compromising%20messages%20to%20Prague%20where%20the%20Czech%20authorities%20seized%20them%20and%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20the%20US.%20Second%2C%20that%20the%20two%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitics-features%2Fwhatsapp-imessage-facebook-apple-fbi-privacy-1261816%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eused%20WhatsApp%20or%20iMessage%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rather%20than%20more%20secure%20messaging%20apps.%20Or%20third%2C%20that%20some%20very%20sophisticated%20surveillance%20technology%20was%20deployed%20against%20the%20Indian%20duo%20%E2%80%93%20presumably%20by%20the%20National%20Security%20Agency%20(NSA)%20%E2%80%93%20once%20the%20assassination%20plot%20came%20on%20to%20the%20DEA%2FFBI%E2%80%99s%20radar%2C%20which%20granted%20their%20investigators%20access%20to%20current%20and%20earlier%20messages%2C%20including%20deleted%20ones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWas%20this%20what%20Trudeau%20meant%20by%20%E2%80%98credible%20allegations%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20violation%20of%20basic%20tradecraft%2C%20CC1%20allowed%20the%20%E2%80%98official%E2%80%99%20nature%20of%20the%20assignment%20to%20become%20more%20than%20apparent%20not%20just%20to%20Gupta%2C%20which%20may%20have%20been%20unavoidable%2C%20but%20also%20to%20the%20hired%20%E2%80%98criminals%E2%80%99.%20Thanks%20to%20messages%20he%20sent%20and%20information%20he%20shared%20with%20Gupta%2C%20who%20relayed%20them%20on%2C%20the%20indictment%20notes%20that%20the%20hitman%20was%20told%20not%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20during%20a%20short%20window%20in%20June%20(when%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20due%20to%20pay%20a%20state%20visit%20to%20Washington)%20but%20either%20before%20or%20after%20that.%20More%20damagingly%2C%20CC1%20shared%20incriminating%20evidence%20about%20the%20murder%20of%20Hardeep%20Nijjar%20in%20Burnaby%20near%20Vancouver%20on%20June%2018%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22182025%2Fdownload-11.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22704%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22394%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20indictment%20now%20helps%20fill%20the%20missing%20links%20in%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20sensational%20September%202023%20statement%20that%20his%20government%20believes%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20linking%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20Ottawa%20has%20refused%20to%20say%20anything%20further%20in%20public%20and%20has%20also%20avoided%20sharing%20some%20of%20the%20information%20it%20has%20with%20India%20citing%20the%20need%20to%20preserve%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20judicial%20proceedings.%20Since%20there%20has%20been%20no%20arrest%20or%20indictment%20in%20Canada%20yet%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20Canadian%20officials%20had%20the%20Pannun%20case%20in%20mind%20and%20that%20at%20least%20some%20%E2%80%93%20if%20not%20the%20major%20%E2%80%93%20part%20of%20the%20intelligence%20linking%20India%20to%20Nijjar%20has%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20electronic%20messages%20the%20US%20has%20captured%20between%20CC1%20and%20Gupta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20all%20the%20details%20in%20the%20indictment%20amount%20to%20allegations%20in%20legal%20terms%20and%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20tested%20before%20a%20judge%20and%20jury.%20Nevertheless%2C%C2%A0%20the%20fact%20that%20three%20key%20federal%20agencies%20or%20departments%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20the%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Agency%20%E2%80%93%20have%20signed%20on%20to%20them%20means%20the%20Biden%20administration%20believes%20the%20evidence%20in%20hand%20is%20credible%20and%20it%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment%20which%20should%20worry%20New%20Delhi.%20If%20some%20of%20the%20evidence%20in%20hand%20has%20been%20harvested%20by%20the%20NSA%2C%20this%20means%20the%20US%20establishment%20has%20invested%20considerable%20resources%20in%20preparing%20the%20case.%20And%20that%20is%20not%20a%20good%20augury%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20has%20assumed%20India%E2%80%99s%20geopolitical%20importance%20will%20help%20it%20weather%20the%20storm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20high%20will%20the%20US%20go%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20India%20is%20not%20just%20an%20%E2%80%98ordinary%E2%80%99%20strategic%20partner%20of%20the%20US%20but%20a%20country%20that%20is%20seen%20by%20diplomats%20on%20both%20sides%20%E2%80%93%20and%20indeed%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20as%20central%20to%20America%E2%80%99s%20global%20interests%20at%20this%20time.%20Given%20the%20larger%20geopolitical%20orchestration%20it%20is%20attempting%20in%20Eurasia%20and%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98Indo-Pacific%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20US%20has%20been%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20overlook%20the%20minor%20dissonances%20with%20India%20that%20have%20cropped%20up%20from%20time%20to%20time%20%E2%80%93%20the%20purchase%20of%20S-400s%20or%20oil%20from%20Russia%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%2C%20under%20Modi%2C%20the%20targeting%20of%20minorities%20and%20the%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20press%20freedom.%20But%20an%20attempted%20murder%20on%20US%20soil%20of%20a%20US%20citizen%20is%20clearly%20harder%20to%20stomach%20and%20requires%20some%20accounting%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20unpalatable%20or%20embarrassing%20it%20may%20be%20for%20the%20Modi%20government.%20And%20early%20indications%20are%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20acting%20towards%20the%20US%20in%20the%20manner%20that%20it%20did%20with%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWednesday%E2%80%99s%20indictment%20is%20a%20first%20step%2C%20a%20shot%20across%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20bow.%20As%20with%20the%201976%20car%20bombing%20in%20Washington%20which%20killed%20the%20former%20Chilean%20ambassador%20Orlando%20Letelier%20and%20his%20American%20associate%20Ronni%20Moffitt%2C%20the%20US%20law%20enforcement%20machinery%20is%20obliged%20to%20investigate%20the%20crime%20and%20identify%20the%20triggermen%20even%20if%20they%20acted%20on%20behalf%20of%20an%20ally.%20But%20how%20high%20up%20the%20chain%20of%20command%20they%20will%20seek%20to%20go%20is%20ultimately%20a%20political%20decision.%20The%20Ford%2C%20Carter%20and%20Reagan%20administrations%20knew%20General%20Pinochet%20had%20ordered%20the%20hit%20on%20Letelier.%20Though%20they%20did%20nothing%20to%20touch%20him%2C%20the%20US%20Congress%20embargoed%20all%20arms%20sales%20to%20Chile.%20In%201978%2C%20a%20grand%20jury%20did%20indict%20Manuel%20Contreras%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Chilean%20secret%20service%2C%20DINA%2C%20but%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20military-controlled%20courts%20refused%20to%20extradite%20him.%20Thus%2C%20the%20only%20persons%20prosecuted%20and%20convicted%20were%20a%20DINA%20operative%2C%20Michael%20Townley%2C%20and%20some%20right-wing%20Cuban%20emigres%20who%20planted%20the%20car%20bomb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Pannun%20case%2C%20Gupta%20seems%20destined%20to%20be%20India%E2%80%99s%20Townley%20but%20who%20will%20be%20its%20Contreras%3F%20If%20the%20US%20authorities%20do%20not%20seek%20to%20prosecute%20CC1%2C%20will%20Gupta%2C%20who%20faces%20up%20to%2020%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20spill%20the%20beans%20the%20way%20Townley%20did%2C%20causing%20further%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%3F%20And%20what%20about%20the%20person%20CC1%20identified%20as%20%E2%80%98boss%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20assured%20Gupta%20that%20criminal%20cases%20he%20faced%20in%20Gujarat%20would%20be%20dropped%20if%20he%20had%20Pannun%20killed%3F%20What%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthree%20men%20in%20business%20attire%E2%80%9D%20seated%20with%20Gupta%20around%20a%20conference%20table%20in%20India%2C%20captured%20on%20video%20during%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20undercover%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-timeline-indian-official-plot-kill-khalistan-activists%5C%22%3EUS%20Justice%20Department%E2%80%99s%20Timeline%3A%20How%20Indian%20Official%20%E2%80%98Plotted%E2%80%99%20to%20Kill%20Khalistan%20Activists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%20to%20pay%20high%20price%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssuming%20the%20indictment%20is%20robust%2C%20it%20is%20obvious%20that%20CC1%20was%20acting%20on%20instructions%20from%20above%20and%20that%20even%20the%20bureaucratic%2Fintelligence%20hierarchy%20would%20have%20been%20operating%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20directions%20from%20the%20political%20leadership%20given%20the%20sensitivity%20and%20risk%20of%20conducting%20such%20an%20operation%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Given%20the%20apparent%20business-as-usual%20on%20display%20in%20the%20bilateral%20relationship%20since%20June%2030%2C%20when%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Czech%20authorities%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20what%20the%20US%20had%20already%20learned%20about%20the%20officially-sanctioned%20assassination%20plot%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20buck%20will%20stop%20at%20Gupta%20and%20not%20even%20CC1.%20Certainly%2C%20this%20is%20the%20best%20the%20Modi%20government%20can%20hope%20for.%20While%20US%20prosecutors%20throw%20the%20book%20at%20Gupta%2C%20will%20the%20White%20House%20be%20content%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98rogue%20agent%E2%80%99%20explanation%20from%20the%20Indian%20side%20and%20an%20assurance%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20repeat%20of%20such%20acts%20in%20the%20future%3F%20The%20fact%20that%20US%20secretary%20of%20state%20Anthony%20Blinken%20held%20an%20aside%20with%20his%20Indian%20counterpart%20after%20the%20recent%202%2B2%20meeting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-2-plus-2-meet-us-asks-india-to-join-canada-probe-both-sides-support-israel%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20raise%20the%20need%20for%20India%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20Canadian%20probe%20into%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20means%20Washington%20does%20not%20believe%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20understood%20there%20are%20certain%20red%20lines%20that%20it%20cannot%20cross.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20it%20decides%20not%20to%20go%20after%20CC1%20and%20others%20in%20India%2C%20the%20US%20will%20extract%20its%20price%20in%20other%20ways%20with%20demands%20that%20may%20be%20hard%20to%20resist%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20reducing%20India%E2%80%99s%20room%20for%20manoeuvre%20on%20defence%2C%20diplomatic%20and%20economic%20matters%20where%20the%20two%20sides%20do%20not%20always%20eye%20to%20eye.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20that%20everyone%20in%20India%20ought%20to%20be%20asking%20is%20why%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20put%20the%20country%20in%20such%20a%20vulnerable%20situation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20case%20against%20targeted%20killings%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20armed%20and%20trained%20the%20Liberation%20Tigers%20of%20Tamil%20Eelam%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20separatist%20group%20that%20quickly%20morphed%20into%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20deadliest%20terrorist%20groups.%20It%20has%20also%20admitted%20launching%20%E2%80%98surgical%20strikes%E2%80%99%20on%20alleged%20terrorist%20sites%20inside%20Pakistan%20controlled%20territory.%20But%20India%20has%20never%20so%20far%20been%20associated%20with%20targeted%20assassinations%20abroad.%20Extra-judicial%20killings%20and%20disappearances%20are%20not%20unknown%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpunjab-militancy-enforced-disappearances-fake-encounters%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einside%20Punjab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20India%20but%20unlike%20Israel%2C%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20Russia%20or%20even%20the%20United%20States%20both%20before%20and%20after%209%2F11%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20shown%20no%20appetite%20for%20physically%20targeting%20wanted%20men%20or%20opponents%20overseas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reason%20for%20this%20was%20not%20necessarily%20the%20lack%20of%20capability%20(though%20this%20may%20have%20been%20a%20factor)%20but%20rather%20a%20realistic%20political%20calculation%20about%20the%20associated%20risks%20and%20benefits%20of%20any%20such%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20hardened%20terrorists%20inside%20Pakistan%20that%20India%20would%20like%20to%20take%20out%2C%20for%20example%2C%20but%20there%20is%20always%20a%20risk%20of%20agents%20being%20caught.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20the%20Pakistani%20allegations%20against%20Kulbhushan%20Jadhav%20are%20correct%20but%20if%20they%20are%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20is%20a%20very%20big%20if%2C%20since%20he%20was%20almost%20certainly%20abducted%20from%20Iran%20border%20and%20not%20apprehended%20inside%20Baluchistan%20as%20Islamabad%20claims%20%E2%80%93%20the%20damage%20that%20his%20arrest%20and%20%E2%80%98confession%E2%80%99%20have%20done%20surely%20outweighs%20any%20benefits%20his%20alleged%20deployment%20may%20have%20generated%20for%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fjadhav3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221395%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-150520%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22773%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKulbhushan%20Jadhav%2C%20seen%20here%20making%20his%20second%20%E2%80%98confession%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20video%20recorded%20in%20April%202017%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20and%20released%20by%20DG%2C%20ISPR%20on%20June%2022%2C%202017%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20danger%20that%20targeted%20assassinations%20could%20lead%20to%20an%20escalation%20in%20terrorist%20attacks.%20You%20do%20not%20put%20your%20hand%20into%20the%20beehive%20without%20being%20sure%20you%20have%20protected%20yourself%20against%20a%20vengeful%20swarm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20India%20has%20been%20targeted%20by%20terrorists%20abroad%2C%20the%20government%2C%20unlike%20Israel%2C%20has%20preferred%20to%20rely%20on%20local%20law%20enforcement%20and%20intelligence%20cooperation%20as%20a%20remedy%20and%20not%20pursued%20its%20own%20remedies%20overseas.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20chose%20to%20hang%20the%20jailed%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Liberation%20Front%20leader%20Maqbool%20Butt%20in%20%E2%80%98retaliation%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20JKLF%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20of%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20Ravindra%20Mhatre%2C%20in%20Birmingham%20in%201984.%20Mhatre%E2%80%99s%20killers%20were%20quickly%20arrested%20and%20sentenced%20to%20lengthy%20terms%20in%20jail%20in%20Britain.%20However%2C%20the%20terrorist%20bombing%20of%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20on%20the%20Montreal-Delhi%20route%20over%20the%20Atlantic%20in%201985%20by%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20did%20not%20lead%20to%20speedy%20or%20complete%20justice.%20It%20is%20now%20widely%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20Canadian%20Security%20Intelligence%20Service%20and%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20botched%20up%20the%20investigation%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fact%20that%20has%20always%20rankled%20with%20the%20Indian%20side.%20Worse%2C%20it%20became%20apparent%20that%20Canada%20had%20actually%20been%20warned%20by%20India%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20major%20terrorist%20incident%20that%20year%20but%20had%20failed%20to%20take%20those%20threats%20seriously.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20the%20CSIS%20even%20had%20a%20mole%20among%20the%20plotters%20but%20eventually%20%E2%80%9Cdropped%20the%20ball%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20rise%20and%20fall%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20threat%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20Kanishka%20bombing%20was%20to%20pursue%20a%20scorched%20earth%20policy%20in%20Punjab%20that%20indiscriminately%20targeted%20Khalistani%20extremists%20but%20also%20hundreds%20if%20not%20thousands%20of%20young%20men%20suspected%20of%20involvement.%20The%20police%20acted%20directly%20and%20also%20through%20the%20use%20of%20former%20militants-turned-mercenaries.%20Ten%20years%20later%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20activist%2C%20Jaswant%20Singh%20Khalra%2C%20who%20was%20investigating%20the%20disappearance%20of%20thousands%20of%20young%20men%20and%20collating%20records%20of%20unidentified%20bodies%20disposed%20of%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20cremation%20grounds%2C%20was%20himself%20abducted%20and%20killed%20by%20the%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20head%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20external%20intelligence%20agency%20at%20the%20time%20Nijjar%20was%20killed%20and%20the%20Pannun%20plot%20was%20allegedly%20hatched%20by%20CC1%20was%20a%20former%20Punjab%20police%20officer%2C%20Samant%20Goel.%20Appointed%20RAW%20chief%20in%202019%20for%20a%20two-year%20term%2C%20he%20was%20given%20two%20one-year%20extensions%20in%202021%20and%202022%20and%20retired%20on%20June%2030%2C%202023.%20Post-retirement%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fformer-raw-chief-samant-kumar-goel-gets-z-category-security%2Farticle67277293.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20has%20given%20him%20Z%20category%20security%20cover%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20him%20perhaps%20the%20first%20former%20intelligence%20chief%20to%20be%20provided%20this%20level%20of%20protection.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.ensaaf.org%2Fofficial%2FS0024%2Fdetail%2F%2C%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20documentation%20prepared%20by%20ensaaf.org%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dozens%20of%20enforced%20disappearances%20and%20extrajudicial%20executions%20in%20the%201990s%C2%A0%20were%20%E2%80%9Creportedly%20committed%20under%20his%20command%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SSP)%20in%20various%20jurisdictions%20of%20Punjab.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20was%20effectively%20over%2C%20helped%20in%20part%20by%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20focus%20on%20fuelling%20violence%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Tiny%20pro-Khalistan%20pockets%20continued%20to%20remain%20active%20amongst%20the%20Sikh%20diaspora%2C%20primarily%20in%20Canada.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20activity%20and%20even%20influence%20of%20Sikh%20nationalist%20groups%20has%20seen%20an%20uptick%2C%20helped%20no%20doubt%20by%20the%20growing%20stridency%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20in%20India.%20But%20the%20challenge%20they%20pose%20is%20largely%20of%20optics%20and%20certainly%20not%20of%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20threat%20overblown%20for%20political%20reasons%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20attempts%20by%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20agencies%20and%20Sikh%20extremists%20in%20the%20diaspora%20to%20revive%20terrorism%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20state%20has%20remained%20peaceful.%20If%20anything%2C%20the%20activities%20of%20criminal%20gangs%20and%20drug%20mafias%20pose%20more%20of%20a%20challenge%20to%20law%20and%20order%20than%20the%20remnants%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%2C%20when%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20is%20dormant%2C%20would%20India%20want%20to%20risk%20international%20criticism%20by%20sending%20a%20hit%20squad%20to%20British%20Columbia%20to%20assassinate%20Nijjar%2C%20as%20Canada%20is%20alleging%2C%20and%20recruit%20a%20%E2%80%98narcotics%20trafficker%E2%80%99%20to%20hire%20a%20gunman%20in%20New%20York%20to%20kill%20Pannun%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20answer%20that%2C%20we%20need%20to%20consider%20three%20factors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20keen%20to%20paint%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20as%20larger%20than%20life%20for%20domestic%20political%20reasons.%20It%20did%20this%20during%20the%20historic%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20when%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20suggest%20the%20farmers%20had%20been%20mobilised%20by%20Sikh%20separatist%20elements%20abroad.%20Yes%2C%20the%20Khalistan%20supporters%20jumped%20on%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bandwagon%20but%20the%20Modi%20government%20made%20matters%20worse%20for%20itself%20by%20using%20strong%20arm%20methods%20against%20the%20farmers%20instead%20of%20speedily%20resolving%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPainting%20an%20essentially%20defunct%20movement%20as%20a%20big%20terror%20threat%20allows%20the%20government%20to%20spread%20a%20sense%20of%20siege%20and%20panic%20about%20looming%20terrorism%20and%20justify%20the%20introduction%20of%20more%20draconian%20laws%20and%20administrative%20measures%2C%20intrusive%20surveillance%20and%20censorship.%20The%20overblown%20Khalistan%20threat%20was%20used%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20to%20get%20social%20media%20companies%20to%20take%20down%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Ffarmers-that-twitter-blocked-government-order-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblock%20a%20whole%20variety%20of%20messages%20and%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20those%20that%20were%20essentially%20expressing%20political%20opposition%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EForeign%20adventurism%20for%20domestic%20gain%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20shown%20a%20growing%20appetite%20for%20adventurism%20abroad%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20use%20of%20Indian%20special%20forces%20against%20a%20yacht%20on%20the%20high%20seas%20off%20Goa%20to%20abduct%20and%20hand%20over%20the%20runaway%20daughter%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1054342%2Fwhy-is-india-being-accused-of-abducting-an-arab-princess%5C%22%3EDubai%20ruler%20Sheikh%20Khalifa%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20UAE%20authorities%20and%20the%20use%20of%20hired%20toughs%20to%20kidnap%20the%20fugitive%20diamantaire%20Mehul%20Choksi%20from%20Antigua%20in%20the%20Caribbean.%20The%20role%20of%20India%20is%20both%20of%20these%20operations%20was%20hard%20to%20keep%20secret%20and%20have%20not%20done%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20international%20reputation%20any%20credit.%20The%20Choksi%20rendition%20was%20botched%20and%20the%20Latifa%20operation%20has%20led%20to%20adverse%20comments%20from%20both%20a%20UN%20Working%20Group%20and%20a%20British%20court.%20The%20French%20captain%20of%20Latifa%E2%80%99s%20yacht%20has%20now%20moved%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%20In%20return%20for%20Latifa%E2%80%99s%20illegal%20abduction%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20the%20extradition%20of%20Christian%20Michel%20from%20the%20UAE%20but%20three%20years%20later%20it%20has%20moved%20no%20closer%20to%20implicating%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20in%20the%20Agusta%20Westland%20scam%20as%20it%20had%20hoped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D44VTIGCU1vo%5C%22%3Eghar%20mein%20ghus%20ke%20marenge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(we%20will%20enter%20homes%20and%20kill)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20off-the-books%20adventurism%20is%20aimed%20at%20generating%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20at%20home%20as%20part%20of%20the%20narrative%20of%20Modi%20building%20an%20%E2%80%98assertive%20India%E2%80%99%20that%20the%20world%20can%20no%20longer%20ignore.%20Even%20if%20the%20assassination%20of%20dormant%20Sikh%20extremists%20abroad%20can%20never%20be%20publicly%20acknowledged%2C%20social%20media%20amplification%20ensures%20the%20message%20is%20conveyed%20to%20the%20base%2C%20and%20to%20the%20wider%20public%2C%20without%20any%20negative%20diplomatic%20fallout.%20In%20Israel%2C%20the%20Golda%20Meir%20government%20never%20officially%20confirmed%20it%20had%20ordered%20the%20killing%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20sportspersons%20at%20the%201972%20Munich%20Olympics.%20But%20even%20in%20a%20pre-social%20media%20era%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20use%20the%20killings%20to%20consolidate%20Israeli%20public%20opinion%20behind%20not%20just%20her%20government%20but%20the%20Israeli%20state%E2%80%99s%20wider%20political%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECalculations%20go%20awry%20when%20caught%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20would%20have%20calculated%20that%20this%20strategy%20was%20a%20low%20cost%20one.%20Why%3F%20Because%20the%20dormant%2C%20vanquished%20Khalistan%20movement%20would%20be%20unable%20to%20retaliate.%20And%20because%20the%20use%20of%20hitmen%2C%20presumably%20recruited%20through%20a%20cut-out%20rather%20than%20an%20actual%20operative%2C%20would%20lower%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20detected.%20But%20most%20of%20all%2C%20the%20calculation%20would%20have%20been%20that%20the%20growing%20US-China%20rivalry%20has%20given%20Modi%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20freedom%20to%20pursue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20competence%20in%20national%20security%20management%20has%20come%20back%20to%20bite%20it.%20The%20key%20to%20a%20covert%20operation%20is%20that%20it%20must%20succeed%20in%20its%20objective%2C%20and%20if%20it%20does%20not%2C%20there%20must%20be%20complete%20and%20plausible%20deniability.%20The%20last%20thing%20you%20want%20in%20a%20covert%20operation%20is%20to%20leave%20a%20trail%20of%20evidence%20and%20be%20caught.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThanks%20to%20the%20Latifa%20case%2C%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20brave%20special%20forces%20will%20forever%20have%20to%20live%20down%20the%20ignominy%20of%20having%20illegally%20and%20forcibly%20boarded%20a%20civilian%20vessel%20on%20the%20high%20seas%20and%20abducted%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20had%20committed%20no%20crime%20and%20certainly%20none%20under%20Indian%20jurisdiction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Antigua%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20got%20caught.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20in%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%2C%20if%20the%20latest%20indictment%20unveiled%20in%20New%20York%20passes%20muster%20in%20court%2C%20history%20will%20record%20that%20it%20got%20caught.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701315595000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30090551%2FUntitled-design-11-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20true%2C%20the%20allegations%20by%20three%20US%20federal%20agencies%20that%20an%20Indian%20official%20ordered%20a%20hit%20on%20Pannun%20in%20New%20York%20paint%20an%20unflattering%20picture%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20leadership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Henry%20Kissinger%20Dies%20at%20100%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30084130%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Kissinger%2C%20an%20influential%20and%20controversial%20figure%20in%20US%20foreign%20policy%2C%20has%20died%2C%20aged%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDr.%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%20a%20respected%20American%20scholar%20and%20statesman%2C%20died%20today%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Connecticut%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kissinger%20Associates%20announced%20in%20a%20statement%20late%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20November%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98War%20criminal%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20was%20born%20in%20Germany%20in%201923.%20His%20family%20moved%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%201938%20to%20flee%20the%20Nazi%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20his%20significant%20influence%20on%20US%20foreign%20policy%20under%20Presidents%20Richard%20Nixon%20and%20Gerald%20Ford%2C%20Kissinger%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20is%20marked%20by%20his%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20as%20well%20as%20opening%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20has%20been%20severely%20criticised%20for%20his%20attitude%20towards%20significant%20war%20crimes%20committed%20by%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Hitchens%2C%20for%20one%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fharpers.org%2Farchive%2F2001%2F02%2Fthe-case-against-he